20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F56548dd4c2814476008b5139%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22901%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFamed%20investor%20Michael%20Burry%20isn't%20shorting%20SpaceX.%3Cp%3EAstrid%20Stawiarz%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EMichael%20Burry%2C%20the%20famed%20investor%2C%20says%20he%20won't%20be%20betting%20on%2C%20or%20against%2C%20SpaceX's%20stock.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIn%20a%20Substack%20post%2C%20Burry%20said%20he%20was%20%26quot%3Btempted%26quot%3B%20by%20options%20to%20bet%20against%20SpaceX.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBurry%20has%20previously%20questioned%20SpaceX's%20worth%2C%20saying%20its%20fundamentals%20don't%20match%20its%20valuation.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EMichael%20Burry%2C%20the%20famed%20investor%20behind%20the%20%26quot%3BBig%20Short%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20he's%20staying%20away%20from%20SpaceX's%20red-hot%20stock.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspacex-ipo-live-updates-pricing-spcx-stock-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESpaceX%20went%20public%20last%20week%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20biggest%20IPO%20in%20market%20history%2C%20and%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspacex-stock-market-valuation-surpass-amazon-elon-musk-jeff-bezos-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Estock%20has%20rallied%20sharply%20since%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20rising%20from%20its%20initial%20price%20of%20%24135%20per%20share%20to%20%24202%20at%20Tuesday's%20close%2C%20a%2050%25%20gain%20in%20just%203%20days%20of%20trading.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20Tuesday%20post%20on%20his%20Substack%2C%20Burry%20updated%20followers%20on%20his%20stock%20portfolio%20and%20said%20he%20won't%20be%20betting%20on%20or%20against%20Elon%20Musk's%20rocket%20company%20for%20the%20time%20being.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBurry%20shared%20details%20of%20several%20put%20options%20that%20would%20allow%20him%20to%20bet%20against%20SpaceX's%20stock%2C%20saying%20he%20was%20%26quot%3Btempted%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20wouldn't%20get%20involved.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%20thank%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20not%20involved%20with%20SpaceX%20now.%20Neither%20short%20nor%2C%20ahem%2C%20long%2C%26quot%3B%20Burry%20wrote%20in%20a%20tongue-in-cheek%20allusion%20to%20his%20long-held%20misgivings%20about%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbig-short-michael-burry-spacex-anthropic-ipo-ai-bubble-claude-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBurry%20questioned%20SpaceX's%20potential%20valuation%3C%2Fa%3E%20ahead%20of%20the%20IPO%2C%20saying%20in%20early%20June%20that%20he%20didn't%20believe%20it%20was%20worth%20%241%20trillion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNothing%20in%20that%20S-1%20suggests%20it%20is%20worth%20%241%20trillion%20let%20alone%20%242%20trillion%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote%20in%20a%20subscriber%20chat%20on%20his%20Substack%20at%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20%242.8%20TRILLION%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Emarket%20cap%2C%20SpaceX%2C%20which%20is%20fundamentally%20a%20small%20space%20company%2C%20a%20niche%20telecom%2C%20a%20bedeviled%20social%20media%20company%2C%20and%20a%20Coreweave-light%2C%20has%20less%20than%20%2420%20billion%20in%20total%20revenue%2C%26quot%3B%20Burry%20wrote%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Burry%20isn't%20trading%20options%20in%20SpaceX%2C%20as%20Business%20Insider's%20Joe%20Ciolli%20wrote%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frecord-volume-spacex-stock-price-call-put-options-casino-open-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehis%20%26quot%3BFirst%20Trade%26quot%3B%20newsletter%3C%2Fa%3E%20this%20morning%2C%20lots%20of%20investors%20are.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMore%20than%201.6%20million%20options%20contracts%20were%20traded%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20the%20first%20day%20options%20were%20available.%20That's%20almost%20five%20times%20the%20previous%20first-day%20record%20after%20Facebook's%202012%20IPO.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpaceX%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2271add73c-412e-444e-881f-4df8e268a32e%5C%22%3EBurry's%20SpaceX%20value%20comparisons%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Elon%20Musk%20speaks%20from%20a%20Nasdaq%20desk%20on%20a%20video%20conference%20during%20the%20SpaceX%20IPO.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a2c29c750aa6577af872078%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22533%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESpaceX%20went%20public%20in%20the%20biggest%20IPO%20ever%20last%20week.%3Cp%3EBrendan%20McDermid%2FReuters%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBurry%20continued%20his%20Substack%20post%20by%20sharing%20a%20lengthy%20list%20of%20things%20that%20SpaceX%20is%20worth%20more%20than%20on%20paper.%20These%20included%20the%20whole%20economies%20of%20Russia%2C%20Canada%2C%20and%20Italy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSpaceX's%20market%20cap%20could%20buy%20Page%2C%20Brin%2C%20Bezos%2C%20Zuckerberg%2C%20Ellison%2C%20Arnault%2C%20Huang%2C%20Buffett%2C%20and%20Ortega%20and%20still%20have%20%241%20trillion%20left%20over.%20Those%20are%20the%20numbers%202-10%20richest%20people%20in%20the%20world%2C%20after%20Elon%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote%2C%20continuing%20that%20the%20company's%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Enet%20worth%20could%20%26quot%3Bbuy%20every%20single%20US%20aerospace%20and%20defense%20company%20and%20have%20money%20left%20to%20buy%20every%20gold%20miner%20and%20airline%20in%20the%20world.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20then%20drew%20a%20line%20between%20SpaceX%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwarren-buffett-surprise-interview-berkshire-hathaway-meeting-gambling-nuclear-deepfakes-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EWarren%20Buffett%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20noting%20that%20Musk's%20personal%20net%20worth%20is%20now%20more%20than%20the%20entire%20market%20capitalization%20of%20Berkshire%20Hathaway.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C