queline%20Fernandez%20is%20reportedly%20set%20to%20star%20in%20her%20first%20ever%20out-and-out%20horror%20film%2C%20produced%20by%20Khyati%20Madaan's%20Not%20Out%20Entertainment.%20A%20song%20and%20teaser%20have%20already%20been%20shot%2C%20with%20principal%20photography%20expected%20to%20begin%20by%20the%20end%20of%20this%20month.%20Jacqueline%20will%20next%20be%20seen%20in%20Welcome%20To%20The%20Jungle%2C%20releasing%20June%2026%2C%202026.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20a%20neuroscientist%20worries%20outsourcing%20thinking%20to%20AI%20could%20weaken%20your%20brain's%20defenses%20against%20dementia%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222698%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Vivienne%20Ming%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69ca54048373a547629c77db%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221799%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETheoretical%20neuroscientist%20Vivienne%20Ming.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Vivienne%20Ming%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EA%20neuroscientist%20worries%20some%20people%20are%20letting%20AI%20do%20too%20much%20of%20their%20thinking.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EOver%20time%2C%20she%20says%2C%20that%20could%20weaken%20cognitive%20reserve%2C%20a%20key%20defense%20against%20dementia.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BHow%20you%20use%20AI%2C%20not%20how%20often%2C%20will%20determine%20its%20impact%2C%26quot%3B%20Vivienne%20Ming%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20doesn't%20cause%20dementia%2C%20but%20how%20you%20use%20it%20could%20weaken%20one%20of%20the%20brain's%20core%20defenses%20against%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20the%20warning%20from%20Vivienne%20Ming%2C%20a%20theoretical%20neuroscientist%2C%20the%20chief%20scientist%20at%20the%20Possibility%20Institute%2C%20a%20metascience%20research%20group%2C%20and%20founder%20of%20Socos%20Labs%2C%20an%20AI%20and%20education%20firm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYour%20chatbot%20is%20not%20giving%20you%20Alzheimer's%2C%26quot%3B%20Ming%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20worry%20is%20the%20cumulative%20impact%20of%20chronic%20substitution%3A%20when%20you%20stop%20doing%20the%20cognitive%20work%20because%20something%20will%20do%20it%20for%20you%2C%20you%20stop%20building%20the%20reserve%20that%20protects%20you%20later%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20AI%20has%20swiftly%20become%20an%20integral%20part%20of%20people's%20lives%20and%20careers%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EAI%20researchers%20and%20some%20tech%20leaders%20have%20been%20releasing%20warnings%20about%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eits%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-deskilling-impact-on-worker-skills-productivity-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edeskilling%20effect%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20slow%20erosion%20of%20job%20skills%2C%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-impact-on-thinking-cognitive-skills-researcher-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edecline%20in%20independent%20thinking%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMing%20went%20a%20step%20further%2C%20saying%20that%20repeatedly%20outsourcing%20mental%20effort%20to%20AI%2C%20especially%20among%20young%20people%2C%20could%20have%20real%20implications%20for%20long-term%20brain%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20the%20group%20from%20whom%20I'm%20most%20concerned%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BHow%20you%20use%20AI%2C%20not%20how%20often%2C%20will%20determine%20its%20impact.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20long%20term%2C%20Ming%20worries%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-keep-brain-sharp-avoid-overreliance-ai-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eroutinely%20outsourcing%20thinking%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20AI%20could%20reduce%20cognitive%20engagement%20and%20make%20it%20harder%20to%20build%20cognitive%20reserve%20%E2%80%94%20the%20brain's%20ability%20to%20adapt%20and%20remain%20resilient%20in%20the%20face%20of%20damage%20or%20aging.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20mechanism%20I'm%20describing%20is%20the%20classic%20'use%20it%20or%20lose%20it%2C'%26quot%3B%20Ming%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229f75c364-2888-4d8c-815a-ba8d3bc4ce40%5C%22%3E'GPT%20is%20the%20new%20GPS'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20drive%20her%20point%20home%2C%20Ming%20compared%20the%20effects%20of%20using%20GPS%20and%20an%20AI%20chatbot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EResearchers%20at%20McGill%20University%20in%20Montreal%20found%20in%202020%20that%20people%20with%20greater%20lifetime%20GPS%20experience%20have%20worse%20spatial%20memory%20during%20self-guided%20navigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20four-month%20small%20study%20conducted%20over%20four%20months%20last%20year%2C%20MIT's%20Media%20Lab%20found%20that%20people%20who%20used%20a%20large%20language%20model%20to%20help%20write%20essays%20showed%20weaker%20neural%20connectivity%20than%20participants%20who%20used%20search%20engines%20or%20no%20external%20tools%2C%20and%20often%20couldn't%20accurately%20quote%20passages%20from%20essays%20they%20had%20written%20minutes%20earlier.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20two%20examples%2C%20Ming%20said%2C%20are%20cases%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-human-intelligence-impact-at-work-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecognitive%20offloading%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20surrender%2C%20or%2C%20as%20she%20put%20it%2C%20%26quot%3Bdelegating%20the%20effortful%20part%20of%20a%20task%20to%20an%20external%20system%20so%20your%20own%20networks%20never%20have%20to%20do%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHer%20concern%20in%20both%20cases%20is%20that%20people%20may%20be%20engaging%20key%20brain%20functions%20less%20frequently%2C%20including%20the%20hippocampus%2C%20the%20part%20of%20your%20brain%20that%20is%20responsible%20for%20memory%20and%20learning%2C%20and%20the%20prefrontal%20brain%20networks%20that%20help%20with%20attention%2C%20self-control%2C%20and%20decision-making.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20hippocampus%20and%20prefrontal%20networks%20doing%20that%20work%20are%20precisely%20the%20systems%20that%20matter%20for%20cognitive%20aging%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGPT%20is%20the%20new%20GPS%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added%2C%20referring%20to%20OpenAI's%20chatbot%20ChatGPT%2C%20which%20she%20said%20could%20erode%20cognitive%20skills%20if%20people%20increasingly%20rely%20on%20it%20to%20think%20for%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2244eee69a-a071-4d52-a713-82ff769ac348%5C%22%3EA%20matter%20of%20cognitive%20reserve%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EResearch%20has%20consistently%20linked%20mentally%20stimulating%20activities%20to%20higher%20levels%20of%20cognitive%20reserve%20and%20lower%20dementia%20risk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20analysis%20conducted%20by%20the%20English%20Longitudinal%20Study%20of%20Ageing%20(ELSA)%20in%202020%20on%2012%2C280%20adults%20aged%2050%20and%20older%2C%20found%20that%20older%20people%20with%20higher%20cognitive%20reserve%20can%20expect%20to%20have%20a%2035%25%20lower%20risk%20of%20developing%20dementia%20compared%20to%20those%20with%20lower%20levels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20principle%20that%20lifelong%20mental%20engagement%20delays%20cognitive%20decline%20is%20some%20of%20the%20most%20replicated%20research%20we%20have%2C%26quot%3B%20Ming%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EImportantly%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EMing%20said%20no%20biomarker%20study%20linking%20AI%20use%20to%20dementia%20pathology%20has%20been%20conducted%20yet.%20Most%20of%20the%20data%20right%20now%20is%20%26quot%3Bcorrelational%20or%20short-term%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20she%20thinks%20now%20is%20the%20time%20to%20start%20analyzing%20this%20cohort%2C%20%26quot%3Bwhile%20the%20behavior%20is%20still%20taking%20shape.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBy%20the%20time%20we%20have%20the%20dementia%20data%2C%20a%20generation%20will%20have%20already%20formed%20the%20habit%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-you-use-ai-could-weaken-brain-defense-against-dementia-2026-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1781693893000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a2bedb850aa6577af871e60%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-you-use-ai-could-weaken-brain-defense-against-dementia-2026-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BHow%20you%20use%20AI%2C%20not%20how%20often%2C%20will%20determine%20its%20impact%2C%26quot%3B%20Vivienne%20Ming%2C%20a%20theoretical%20neuroscientist%20and%20AI%20researcher%20told%20Business%20Insider.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22tspirlet%40insider.com%20(Thibault%20Spirlet)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ukraine%20says%20even%20its%20obsolete%20drone-war%20tech%20still%20has%20value%20for%20friendly%20countries%20bracing%20for%20Shahed-style%20attacks%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225779%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Two%20men%20lean%20over%20a%20large%20black%20drone%20on%20grass%20with%20concrete%20bricks%20stacked%20into%20a%20wall%20behind%20them%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a2fd3af0b873a3c9460cad7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223853%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUkraine%20has%20years%20of%20experience%20fighting%20drone%20barrages%2C%20and%20allies%20are%20interested%20in%20its%20counter-drone%20tech.%3Cp%3EIvan%20SAMOILOV%20%2F%20AFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EUkraine's%20fast-moving%20fight%20means%20once-cutting-edge%20defense%20tech%20can%20quickly%20lose%20relevance.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAn%20official%20said%20counter-drone%20tech%20no%20longer%20ideal%20for%20Ukraine%20could%20still%2