ar%2C%20helmets%2C%20and%20face%20scarves%20stand%20under%20trees%2C%20with%20one%20holding%20a%20blue%20interceptor%20drone%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a31459e9ab49a5611720418%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223648%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUkraine%20has%20developed%20new%20counter-drone%20solutions%20that%20allies%20are%20interested%20in.%3Cp%3EFrancisco%20Richart%2FAnadolu%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAloian's%20idea%20aligns%20with%20a%20key%20lesson%20NATO%20nations%20are%20learning%20from%20the%20war%20in%20Ukraine%3A%20having%20a%20lot%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-shows-nato-perfect-weapons-10-years-maybe-late-speed-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Egood-enough%20weapons%3C%2Fa%3E%20available%20today%20beats%20a%20limited%20arsenal%20of%20perfect%20ones%20that%20come%20too%20late.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20deputy%20secretary%20said%20that%20this%20dynamic%20was%20visible%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%20during%20the%20Iran%20war%2C%20when%20the%20US%20and%20its%20Gulf%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspeed-ukraine-battlefield-development-pushes-weapons-makers-modular-software-first-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eallies%20faced%20attacks%20by%3C%2Fa%3E%20Iran's%20Shahed%20drones.%20Though%20Tehran%20used%20some%20newer%20jet-powered%20one-way%20attack%20drones%2C%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Firan-russia-now-us-one-style-drone-reshaping-moden-war-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMoscow%20is%20increasingly%20deploying%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20it%20relied%20heavily%20on%20propeller-driven%20Shahed%20designs%20%E2%80%94%20the%20kind%20that%20Ukraine%20had%20been%20battling%20since%20early%20in%20Russia's%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20Iran%20war%2C%20Ukraine%20sent%20roughly%20200%20military%20experts%20to%20the%20Middle%20East%20to%20help%20nations%20strengthen%20their%20air%20defenses.%20It%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspeed-ukraine-battlefield-development-pushes-weapons-makers-modular-software-first-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ealso%20sent%20troops%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Ukrainian%20anti-drone%20solutions%2C%20which%20were%20used%20in%20combat.%20The%20fight%20triggered%20a%20sharp%20increase%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Firan-shahed-drone-interceptor-booming-business-manufacturers-middle-east-t2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Einterest%20in%20interceptor%20drones%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAloian%20said%20that%20designs%20that%20were%20a%20year%20old%20and%20less%20relevant%20at%20home%20still%20proved%20effective%20in%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20ready%20to%20share%20our%20operation%2C%20technologies%2C%20and%20experience%2C%20and%20everything%20that%20will%20be%20needed%20in%20order%20for%20our%20partners%20to%20achieve%20the%20same%20level%20of%20defense%20deterrence%20that%20we%20have%20in%20Ukraine%2C%26quot%3B%20Aloian%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20starting%20place%20could%20be%20gear%20that%20Ukraine%20no%20longer%20has%20use%20for%20but%20could%20still%20prove%20practical%20for%20another%20operator%20in%20another%20kind%20of%20fight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAloian%20said%20it%20would%20be%20useful%20for%20allies%20to%20have%20%26quot%3Baccess%20to%20those%20solutions%20that%20are%20efficient.%26quot%3B%20Even%20if%20they're%20not%20used%20in%20a%20fight%2C%20they%20could%20hold%20value%20as%20training%20tools%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUkrainian%20officials%20have%20said%20that%20Kyiv%20is%20willing%20to%20send%20partner%20nations%20defense%20technology%2C%20including%20interceptors%2C%20when%20it%20can%20do%20so%20without%20hurting%20its%20fight.%20It%20is%20also%20planning%20to%20export%20some%20systems%2C%20including%20long-range%20drones%2C%20that%20are%20no%20longer%20useful%20on%20its%20battlefield%20but%20still%20interest%20partners.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAloian%20said%20that%20in%20the%20war%20with%20Russia%2C%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspeed-ukraine-battlefield-development-pushes-weapons-makers-modular-software-first-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Espeed%20is%20essential%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20defense%20industry%20has%20to%20work%20much%20faster%20than%20what%20allies%20are%20used%20to.%20Within%20months%2C%20%26quot%3Bsolutions%20will%20already%20be%20outdated.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%228192%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Two%20men%20in%20camouflage%20trousers%20and%20green%20t-shirts%20walk%20in%20a%20field%20with%20their%20backs%20turned%2C%20holding%20a%20large%20black%20drone%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a3145fc9ab49a561172041d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225464%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUkraine%20is%20developing%20a%20host%20of%20new%20drone%20technologies%20and%20says%20the%20battlefield%20changes%20so%20fast%20that%20they%20can%20become%20outdated%20in%20weeks%20and%20months.%3Cp%3EYevhen%20Titov%2FGlobal%20Images%20Ukraine%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EUkrainian%20officials%20have%20said%20that%20interceptor%20drone%20designs%20can%20change%20so%20quickly%20that%20the%20advantage%20of%20a%20new%20model%20may%20be%20negated%20within%20months.%20Companies%20are%20constantly%20upgrading%20platforms%20while%20swiftly%20phasing%20out%20obsolete%20systems.%20There%20are%20possibilities%20for%20those%20systems%2C%20though%2C%20in%20regions%20like%20the%20Middle%20East%20or%20elsewhere%20in%20Europe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENATO%20countries%20are%20increasingly%20concerned%20about%20drones%2C%20especially%20after%20several%20Russian%20long-range%20drone%20incursions%2C%20but%20they%20are%20not%20under%20the%20same%20immediate%20pressure%20as%20Ukraine%2C%20which%20faces%20bombardments%20regularly.%20Officials%20have%20argued%20that%2C%20as%20they%20prepare%20for%20future%20drone%20threats%2C%20there%20is%20real%20value%20in%20defenses%20that%20are%20available%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUkraine%20has%20shifted%20from%20being%20a%20country%20many%20expected%20to%20be%20quickly%20overrun%20by%20Russia%20and%20urgently%20seeking%20help%20from%20cautious%20partners%20to%20being%20a%20source%20of%20new%20battlefield%20technology%20and%20tactical%20lessons%20that%20many%20Western%20militaries%20now%20want%20to%20study.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAloian%20said%20Ukraine%20has%20%26quot%3Bthe%20experience%2C%20and%20we%20have%20the%20knowledge%2C%20we%20have%20the%20solutions%26quot%3B%20that%20it's%20already%20sharing%20%26quot%3Bwith%20our%2C%20not%20even%20partners%2C%20but%20with%20friends.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-says-even-outdated-drone-tech-can-work-allies-2026-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1781693763000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a2fd3d70b873a3c9460cad9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-says-even-outdated-drone-tech-can-work-allies-2026-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20Ukrainian%20official%20says%20drone%20tech%20that%20is%20aging%20out%20of%20his%20country's%20fast-moving%20fight%20could%20still%20help%20partners%20preparing%20for%20similar%20attacks.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22sbaker%40insider.com%20(Sin%C3%A9ad%20Baker)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kishan%20eclipses%20Maxwell's%20famous%20Wankhede%20hundred%2C%20hits%2071-ball%20ton%20to%20become%20...%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1781693743000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-131796969%2Cimgsize-58466.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcric