l.%3Cp%3EBose%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EA%20version%20of%20this%20post%20appears%20in%20the%20CMO%20Insider%20newsletter.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESign%20up%20for%20%3Ca%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsubscription%2Fnewsletter%2Fcmo-insider%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider's%20weekly%20marketing%20newsletter%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EBose%20wants%20a%20bigger%20chunk%20of%20the%20music%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fbest-bose-headphones%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eaudio-equipment%20maker%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20created%20Bose%20Studios%2C%20an%20in-house%20content%20studio%20designed%20to%20help%20it%20shift%20from%20campaign-driven%20marketing%2C%20the%20company%20%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3Eexclusively%20told%20CMO%20Insider.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20key%20differentiator%20is%20the%20launch%20of%20a%20new%20record%20label%2C%20Bose%20Records.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcmo-jim-mollica-bose-luxury-marketing-business-growth-cannes-lions-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBose%20CMO%20Jim%20Mollica%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20in%20an%20interview%20that%20the%20plan%20isn't%20to%20go%20toe-to-toe%20with%20the%20%26quot%3BBig%20Three%26quot%3B%20label%20conglomerates%2C%20but%20rather%20to%20help%20break%20underappreciated%20or%20new%20artists%20and%20%E2%80%94%20crucially%20%E2%80%94%20not%20have%20to%20pay%20for%20music%20rights%20when%20they%20feature%20in%20Bose%20commercials.%20(Mollica%20said%20Bose%20wouldn't%20look%20to%20own%20the%20artists'%20masters%2C%20the%20company%20wouldn't%20take%20a%20share%20of%20their%20record%20sales%20or%20streams%2C%20and%20that%20they%20would%20be%20free%20to%20sign%20with%20other%20labels.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20big%20projects%20include%20commissioning%20original%20TV%20series%20and%20films%20%26quot%3Battached%20to%20some%20legendary%20Hollywood%20names%2C%26quot%3B%20Mollica%20said.%20Bose%20is%20also%20planning%20a%20YouTube%20series%2C%20podcasts%2C%20and%20live%20music%20events%20%E2%80%94%20and%20could%20perhaps%20even%20buy%20a%20music%20media%20company.%20Some%20of%20those%20properties%20will%20generate%20their%20own%20ad%20revenue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20launch%20of%20Bose%20Studios%20reflects%20a%20reality%20most%20CMOs%20face.%20Ad%20prices%20are%20higher%2C%20even%20though%20audiences%20are%20more%20fragmented%20and%2C%20in%20the%20case%20of%20TV%2C%20smaller.%20Consumers%20are%20actively%20avoiding%20advertising.%20Social%20media%20algorithms%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-search-reshapes-seo-fueling-geo-gold-rush-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Erise%20of%20AI%20search%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20disrupting%20the%20old%20ways%20that%20brands%20were%20discovered.%20Brands%20need%20to%20entertain%20to%20cut%20through.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20category%2C%20music%2C%20has%20a%20bunch%20of%20rituals%20baked%20into%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Mollica%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20we%20have%20the%20opportunity%2C%20not%20to%20sell%20products%2C%20but%20become%20part%20of%20that%20ritual%2C%20then%20ultimately%20Bose%20is%20not%20an%20audio-equipment%20business%20anymore.%20We're%20about%20deepening%20people's%20relationship%20with%20music.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMuch%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-helps-give-bose-customers-the-right-experience-of-the-brand-says-cmo-jim-mollica-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBose's%20prior%20marketing%3C%2Fa%3E%20already%20focused%20on%20forging%20partnerships%20with%20music%20artists.%20Last%20year%2C%20for%20example%2C%20it%20teamed%20up%20with%20Blackpink's%20LISA%20to%20create%20customized%20earbuds%2C%20which%20it%20launched%20at%20a%20pop-up%20store%20in%20Los%20Angeles.%20This%20past%20February%2C%20it%20collaborated%20with%20the%20Grammy-nominated%20Twitch%20streamer%20PlaqueBoyMax%2C%20who%20created%20music%20on%20the%20spot%20during%20a%20livestream%20that%20aired%20during%20the%20NBA's%20All-Star%20weekend.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20record%20label%20and%20film%20productions%20signal%20Bose's%20expanded%20ambitions.%20Other%20brands%2C%20including%20Red%20Bull%20and%20Starbucks%2C%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstarbucks-fun-facts-2018-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elaunched%20music%20labels%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20past%2C%20though%20they%20were%20eventually%20retired.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlexandra%20Annable%2C%20founder%20of%20Holl'r%20Music%2C%20an%20artist%20management%20and%20booking%20agency%2C%20said%20competition%20is%20fiercer%20than%20ever%20for%20emerging%20artists.%20For%20Bose%20to%20succeed%2C%20it%20might%20want%20to%20consider%20aligning%20itself%20with%20a%20specific%20genre%2C%20she%20added%2C%20pointing%20to%20Wingstop%2C%20which%20created%20its%20UK%20Freestyle%20Series%20for%20emerging%20drill%2C%20rap%2C%20and%20hip-hop%20artists.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20the%20only%20way%20brands%20can%20effectively%20engage%20with%20music%20fans%20is%20to%20create%20unique%2C%20content-led%20experiences%2C%20but%20these%20must%20be%20really%20authentic%20and%20culturally%20relevant%2C%26quot%3B%20Annable%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESteve%20Ackerman%2C%20a%20board%20advisor%20and%20consultant%20to%20media%20and%20entertainment%20businesses%2C%20said%20Bose%20Studios%20needs%20to%20ensure%20the%20content%20comes%20before%20promoting%20its%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20graveyard%20of%20branded%20content%20is%20littered%20with%20brands%20that%20have%20gone%20down%20this%20route%20and%20not%20understood%20what%20it%20means%20to%20be%20a%20content%20creator%2C%26quot%3B%20Ackerman%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey%20often%20defaulted%20to%20advertising%20agencies%20that%20don't%20understand%20how%20to%20engage%20with%20audiences%3B%20they%20just%20understand%20how%20to%20create%20content%20that%20gets%20in%20the%20way%20of%20the%20thing%20that%20audiences%20want%20to%20engage%20with.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMollica%2C%20who%20previously%20worked%20at%20Disney%20and%20Viacom%2C%20said%20he%20understands%20the%20assignment.%20He%20said%20Bose%20Studios%20is%20not%20working%20with%20ad%20agencies%20and%20is%20recruiting%20and%20partnering%20with%20talent%20across%20the%20film%2C%20TV%2C%20podcast%2C%20and%20publishing%20industries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20isn't%20product%20placement%3B%20this%20isn't%20a%20long%2C%2030-minute%20commercial%2C%26quot%3B%20Mollica%20said.%20%26quot%3BThese%20things%20are%20truly%20about%20how%20we%20are%20taking%20this%20authentic%20love%20of%20music%20and%20elevating%20the%20content%20that's%20out%20there%20today%20for%20true%20music%20fans%20to%20experience%20more.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbose-becoming-media-company-launching-record-label-2026-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1781691960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a325e844074dae0e20447fd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbose-becoming-media-company-launching-record-label-2026-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bose%20is%20launching%20a%20new%20entertainment%20division%2C%20Bose%20Studios%2C%20which%20includes%20the%20creation%20of%20a%20record%20label.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22loreilly%40insider.com%20(Lara%20O'Reilly)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A99%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Telegram%20under%20scrutiny%20again%3A%20What%20makes%20it%20different%20from%20messaging%20apps%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1781691946000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2F