ide%20the%20container%20into%20the%20air%20fryer's%20grooves%2C%20and%20it's%20ready%20to%20cook.%20I%20appreciate%20the%20Max%20Crisp%20and%20recrisp%20options.%20I%E2%80%99ve%20reheated%20leftovers%20or%20re-crisped%20takeout%20many%20times.%20It%20might%20be%20its%20best%20feature%20and%20often%20overlooked%20on%20many%20air%20fryers.%20It%20was%20especially%20useful%20on%20nights%20when%20dinner%20happened%20in%20shifts%20because%20of%20kids%E2%80%99%20sports%20and%20work%20schedules.%20Everyone%20could%20still%20get%20crispy%20nuggets%2C%20fries%2C%20or%20leftovers%2C%20no%20matter%20when%20they%20sat%20down%20to%20eat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20store%20the%20glass%20container%20with%20the%20motor%20and%20keep%20the%20extra%20container%20in%20your%20cabinet%20or%20nest%20the%20smaller%20container%20inside%20the%20larger%20one.%20The%20glass%20design%20actually%20makes%20cooking%20easier%2C%20and%20they%E2%80%99re%20easy%20to%20transfer%20from%20the%20fridge%20to%20the%20counter%20to%20the%20table.%20Being%20able%20to%20see%20food%20through%20the%20glass%20helped%20prevent%20overcooking.%20Mostly%20though%2C%20it%20was%20just%20fun%20to%20watch%20the%20time-lapse%20of%20pale-yellow%20fries%20turning%20golden%20and%20crunchy%2C%20like%20my%20own%20personal%20cooking%20show.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22two%20glass%20containers%20on%20top%20of%20each%20other%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a31c512564c774507cd3391%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELids%20make%20it%20easy%20to%20store%20leftovers%20directly%20in%20the%20fridge.%3Cp%3EJennifer%20Zyman%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EEach%20comes%20with%20a%20matching%20plastic%20lid%20so%20you%20can%20store%20prepped%20ingredients%20or%20leftovers%20in%20the%20fridge.%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20find%20that%20prepping%20ingredients%20in%20the%20same%20vessel%20was%20a%20good%20idea%20if%20I%20wanted%20things%20to%20be%20crisp%2C%20since%20the%20added%20moisture%20from%20marinades%20was%20a%20deterrent%20to%20crispness.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22893982bb-00c9-492d-9503-cd4165a55553%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Cooking%20performance%5C%22%3EThe%20glass%20design%20drew%20me%20in%2C%20but%20the%20crisping%20performance%20is%20what%20made%20me%20keep%20using%20it.%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222400%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Crinkle-cut%20fries%20and%20roasted%20Brussels%20sprouts%20sit%20in%20glass%20air-fryer%20baskets%20on%20a%20kitchen%20counter.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a3183afe826bfa433d6e8fb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMy%20perfectly%20crisped%20fries%20and%20brussel%20sprouts%3Cp%3EJennifer%20Zyman%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Crispi%20Pro%20did%20an%20excellent%20job%20of%20evenly%20browning%20and%20crisping%20the%20food.%20During%20testing%2C%20I%20often%20used%20it%20to%20finish%20foods%20that%20other%20air%20fryers%20struggled%20with.%20For%20instance%2C%20during%20a%20chicken%20wing%20test%2C%20another%20brand%20failed%20to%20get%20the%20skin%20as%20crisp%20as%20I%20wanted%2C%20so%20I%20moved%20them%20to%20the%20Ninja%20Crispi%20Pro%2C%20where%20they%20finished%20beautifully%2C%20saving%20dinner%20time.%20Even%20with%20the%20requisite%20shaking%20and%20flipping%2C%20some%20items%20with%20more%20inherent%20moisture%2C%20such%20as%20fresh%20chicken%20wings%2C%20took%20longer%20to%20cook%20than%20in%20the%20basket-style%20models%20we%20tested.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20possibilities%2C%20I%20encourage%20people%20to%20think%20beyond%20the%20chicken%20wings%20and%20French%20fries%20that%20these%20machines%20are%20so%20good%20for.%20I%20used%20both%20containers%20to%20make%20a%20pork%20tenderloin%20and%20Brussels%20sprouts%20one%20night%2C%20and%20Japanese%20sweet%20potatoes%20the%20next.%20It%20can%20really%20do%20a%20lot%20more%20than%20foods%20that%20come%20in%20bags%20meant%20for%20the%20freezer.%20It%20is%20also%20great%20for%20reheating%20leftovers%20if%20you%20are%20someone%20who%20would%20rather%20not%20use%20a%20microwave.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20caveat%20with%20the%20Ninja%20Crispi%20Pro%20is%20that%20the%20glass%20can%20sometimes%20produce%20too%20much%20moisture%2C%20which%20can%20work%20against%20cooking%20when%20you%20want%20very%20dry%20heat.%20The%20way%20to%20avoid%20this%20is%20to%20avoid%20overcrowding%20the%20containers.%20Yet%2C%20I%20do%20find%20the%20containers%20are%20sometimes%20a%20deterrent%2C%20as%20you%20can%20only%20fit%20so%20much%20into%20the%20large%20container%20compared%20to%20other%20basket%20fires%20with%20dividers%20or%20other%20mechanisms%2C%20like%20dual%20baskets%2C%20which%20let%20you%20spread%20out%20the%20hot%2C%20dry%20air.%20So%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20spacious%2C%20but%20a%20divider%20of%20some%20sort%20would%20help%20it%20accommodate%20more%2C%20since%20you%20can%20only%20fit%20so%20much%20in%20this%20style.%20You%20get%20a%20lot%20more%20real%20estate%20for%20chicken%20wings%20in%20a%20basket%20style.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220709614c-af7e-46ea-971b-64b0a78144c1%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22What%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20love%5C%22%3EWhat%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20love%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22water%20droplets%20trapped%20between%20the%20glass%20and%20handle%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a31c51b2bbd1d834ef245de%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWater%20droplets%20get%20caught%20between%20the%20integrated%20handles%20and%20glass%20and%20is%20hard%20to%20properly%20dry.%3Cp%3EJennifer%20Zyman%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e067c5f9-da7d-4b91-aefb-f4db56a62d8c%5C%22%3ECleanup%20is%20where%20the%20design%20works%20against%20it%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20it%20seems%20like%20cleanup%20would%20be%20easier%20with%20a%20glass%20air%20fryer%2C%20I%20found%20it%20more%20difficult%20than%20with%20other%20designs.%20The%20glass%20containers%20have%20integrated%2C%20non-removable%20handles%2C%20and%20while%20they%20can%20go%20in%20the%20dishwasher%2C%20they%20never%20look%20fully%20clean.%20There's%20always%20some%20discoloration.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20integrated%20handles%20also%20make%20drying%20more%20difficult.%20Moisture%20can%20get%20trapped%20between%20the%20handle%20attachment%20and%20the%20glass%20exterior.%20No%20matter%20how%20well%20you%20air-dry%20it%2C%20water%20lingered%2C%20creating%20a%20breeding%20ground%20for%20bacteria.%20I%20hope%20Ninja%20addresses%20this%20design%20issue%2C%20which%20was%20also%20a%20problem%20with%20the%20initial%20Crispi%20air%20fryer%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20reason%20I%20gave%20that%20one%20away.%20This%20is%20a%20real%20problem%20the%20brand%20needs%20to%20address%20because%20it%20affects%20my%20overall%20satisfaction%20with%20this%20product.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221dd17cb4-9041-44fd-b6b4-cf7a09ae0e71%5C%22%3EThe%20multi-part%20design%20makes%20storage%20less%20convenient%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20also%20much%20more%20awkward%20to%20pick%20up%20and%20store%2C%20with%20its%20multiple%20parts%2C%20compared%20to%20a%20basket%20air%20fryer.%20There%20are%20multiple%20pieces%20to%20manage%2C%20and%20the%20unit%20is%20heavy%20enough%20that%20I%20would%20not%20recommend%20it%20for%20anyone%20with%20mobility%20concerns%20or%20anyone%20who%20needs%20to%20move%20their%20appliances%20in%20and%20out%20of%20storage%20frequently.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20it%20is%20much%20more%20expensive%20than%20standard%20air%20fryers%2C%20even%20its%20little%20sister.%20Ninja%20uses%20%26quot%3Bnon-toxic%26quot%3B%20as%20a%20claim%2C%20but%20we%20are%20not%20sure%20of%20its%20validity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222b23c2d7-9d39-422d-a0ef-8c7e929d580f%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Alternatives%20to%20consider%5C%22%3EAlternatives%20to%20consider%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222400%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Two%20countertop%20air%20fryers%20sit%20side%20by%20side%20on%20kitchen%20counters%2C%20including%20a%20COSORI%20unit%20and%20an%20Instant%20Vortex%20Plus%20unit.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a3184e0e826bfa433d6e90e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETwo%20of%20our%20other%20favorite%20high-performing%20models%20include%20the%20Cosori%20TurboBlaze%2C%20our%20best%20overall%2C%20and%20the%20Instant%20Vortex%20Plus%2C%20which%20has%20a%20glass%20viewing%20window.%3Cp%3EJennifer%20Zyman%3B%20James%20Brains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20aren't%20many%20other%20glass-based%20air%20fryers%2C%20but%20these%20are%20good%20choices%20if%20the%20Pro%20isn't%20for%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20are%20not%20bothered%20by%20plastic%20or%20are%20looking%20for%20a%20glass%20air%20fryer%2C%20I%20also%20recommend%20the%20%3Ca%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3Fh%3Dffcabbbe2c84e501efc0781e15b367130bad65cd5fd7ba3e88fdd5c243650624%26postID%3D6a317618778476c08ac907e6%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fkitchen%252Fninja-crispi-pro-review%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252Fdp%252FB0C33CHG99%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECosori%20TurboBlaze%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20won%20our%20best%20overall%20category%20during%20my%20air%20fryer%20testing.%20It%20is%20only%20%24120%2C%20and%20the%20TurboBlaze%20technology%20is%20not%20false%20advertising.%20This%20air%20fryer%20cooks%20food%20accurately%20and%20quickly.%20I%20also%20appreciated%20the%20sleek%20digital%20display%20and%20how%20easy%20it%20was%20to%20move%20out%20of%20the%20way%20when%20not%20in%20use.%20We%20also%20like%20the%20%3Ca%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3Fh%3D0f61dbfeee0de53372983f63b516f47cf6ace52d2ddcebc2770435400c3f1cb9%26postID%3D6a317618778476c08ac907e6%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fkitchen%252Fninja-crispi-pro-review%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252FInstant-Technology-Functions-Dehydrates-Reheats%252Fdp%252FB096N28SZP%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EInstant%20Vortex%20Plus%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20has%20a%20glass%20viewing%20window%20to%20monitor%20food%20progress%2C%20and%20the%20model%20we%20tested%20has%20odor-erasing%20technology%20that%20absorbs%20lingering%20food%20smells.%20Read%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fkitchen%2Finstant-vortex-plus-air-fryer-reviewhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fkitchen%2Finstant-vortex-plus-air-fryer-review%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EInstant%20Vortex%20Plus%20review%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226ef4c1a2-50ca-4681-b595-c2501933e39b%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22The%20bottom%20line%5C%22%3EThe%20bottom%20line%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22fries%20in%20the%20air%20fryer%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a31822f6a1225644000d380%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Ninja%20Crispi%20Pro%20gets%20food%20perfectly%20crispy%20and%20is%20convenient%20to%20monitor%20food%20progress.%3Cp%3EJennifer%20Zyman%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Ninja%20Crispi%20Pro%20is%20not%20just%20an%20air%20fryer%20for%20people%20who%20want%20to%20watch%20their%20fries%20get%20crispy.%20It%20is%20an%20air%20fryer%20for%20people%20who%20may%20have%20concerns%20about%20their%20air%20fryer%20basket.%20The%20glass%20containers%20make%20air%20fryer%20cooking%20feel%20more%20transparent%20and%20make%20leftovers%20easier%20to%20manage.%20While%20I%20would%20not%20call%20it%20a%20perfect%20or%20completely%20coating-free%20solution%2C%20it%20is%20a%20genuinely%20compelling%20solution%20for%20those%20looking%20to%20reduce%20plastic%20in%20the%20kitchen.%20Plus%2C%20it%20is%20super%20powerful%20to%20boot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20should%20buy%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThose%20looking%20to%20reduce%20plastic%20in%20their%20kitchen.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ECooks%20who%20want%20to%20watch%20their%20dishes%20in%20progress.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESomeone%20who%20wants%20to%20prep%2C%20cook%2C%20and%20store%20in%20the%20same%20container.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20should%20skip%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThose%20with%20mobility%20concerns%20find%20it%20awkward%20to%20move.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EPeople%20who%20don't%20want%20any%20semblance%20of%20a%20nonstick%20coating.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ECooks%20who%20need%20more%20capacity%20for%20larger%20families.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fkitchen%2Fninja-crispi-pro-review%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1781690402000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69fe5cf9e1443b8dc48e37de%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fkitchen%2Fninja-crispi-pro-review%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ninja's%20Crispi%20Pro%20is%20a%20powerful%20glass%20air%20fryer%20that%20reduces%20reliance%20on%20nonstick%20baskets%20and%20aced%20our%20cooking%20tests%2C%20but%20it%20has%20one%20major%20trade%20off.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Jennifer%20Zyman)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Allbirds%20is%20now%20Smartbirds%2C%20and%20its%20AI-focused%20CEO%20says%20people%20won't%20even%20remember%20the%20shoes'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Nadia%20Carlston%20has%20just%20been%20named%20as%20CEO%20of%20Smartbird%2C%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a30a15d9ab49a56117201c1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ENadia%20Carlston%20has%20just%20been%20named%20as%20CEO%20of%20Smartbird.%3Cp%3ESmartbird%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAllbirds%20has%20been%20rebranded%20as%20Smartbird.%20Instead%20of%20selling%20shoes%2C%20it's%20an%20AI%20infrastructure%20provider.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ENadia%20Carlsten%2C%20the%20new%20CEO%2C%20spoke%20exclusively%20to%20Business%20Insider%20about%20her%20plans.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EShe%20wants%20to%20build%20custom%2C%20single-tenant%20AI%20infrastructure%20for%20mid-market%20enterprises.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20few%20years%20ago%2C%20Allbirds%20was%20Silicon%20Valley's%20favorite%20sneaker%20company.%20Now%20it's%20betting%20its%20future%20on%20AI%20infrastructure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20selling%20off%20its%20footwear%20business%20and%20shedding%20most%20of%20its%20workforce%2C%20the%20company%20formerly%20known%20for%20its%20eco-friendly%20wool%20sneakers%20has%20reinvented%20itself%20as%20Smartbird%2C%20an%20AI%20infrastructure%20provider%20led%20by%20a%20CEO%20who%20has%20never%20worn%20its%20signature%20shoes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20transformation%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20dramatic%20pivots%20of%20the%20AI%20boom%20and%20a%20test%20of%20whether%20a%20struggling%20public%20consumer%20company%20can%20transition%20into%20an%20AI%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20more%20of%20a%20high%20heels%20person%20myself%2C%26quot%3B%20Nadia%20Carlsten%20told%20Business%20Insider%20in%20an%20exclusive%20interview.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20blissfully%20unaware%20of%20all%20things%20Allbirds.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20those%20unaware%2C%20Allbirds%20launched%20in%202015%20and%20quickly%20became%20one%20of%20tech's%20hottest%20consumer%20brands%2C%20with%20its%20sneakers%20as%20much%20a%20part%20of%20the%20Silicon%20Valley%20uniform%20as%20hoodies%20and%20Patagonia%20vests.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20going%20public%20in%202021%2C%20Allbirds%20was%20worth%20nearly%20%244%20billion.%20But%20the%20brand's%20cool%20factor%20faded%20almost%20as%20quickly%20as%20it%20arrived.%20By%20early%202025%2C%20Allbirds'%20market%20value%20had%20fallen%20below%20%2420%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20in%20April%2C%20the%20company%20announced%20an%20only-in-2026%20pivot%3A%20It%20would%20no%20longer%20sell%20shoes%20and%20instead%20become%20an%20AI%20infrastructure%20provider%2C%20going%20head-to-head%20with%20the%20likes%20of%20Amazon%2C%20CoreWeave%2C%20and%20Crusoe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20ridiculed%20the%20move%20as%20%26quot%3Bbizarre%2C%26quot%3B%20or%20even%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fstocktwits.com%2Fnews-articles%2Fmarkets%2Fequity%2Fbird-stock-surge-on-ai-hype-is-ridiculous-and-concerning-says-veteran-investor-george-noble%2FcZJ6WOpRIUA%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3Bridiculous%20and%20concerning.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffinance.yahoo.com%2Fmarkets%2Fstocks%2Farticles%2Fallbirds-bizarre-pivot-shoes-ai-230714084.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3C%2Fa%3EWall%20Street%20was%20more%20enthusiastic%2C%20with%20the%20stock%20briefly%20soaring%20800%25%20on%20the%20news%2C%20though%20it%20has%20since%20lost%20much%20of%20its%20gains.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225904%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sneakers%20displayed%20at%20an%20Allbirds%20store%20in%20the%20Georgetown%20neighborhood%20of%20Washington%2C%20D.C.%2C%20U.S.%2C%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20Feb.%2016%2C%202021.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a317848e826bfa433d6e872%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223936%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESneakers%20displayed%20at%20an%20Allbirds%20store%20in%20the%20Georgetown%20neighborhood%20of%20Washington%2C%20D.C.%2C%20U.S.%2C%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20Feb.%2016%2C%202021.%3Cp%3EBloomberg%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20transformation%20became%20official%20on%20Wednesday%20as%20the%20company%20said%20that%20it%20has%20completed%20the%20sale%20of%20the%20Allbirds%20brand%20and%20footwear%20assets%2C%20changed%20its%20legal%20name%20to%20Smartbird%2C%20and%20appointed%20Carlsten%20as%20president%20and%20CEO.%20She%20replaces%20Joe%20Vernachio%2C%20who%20is%20resigning%20from%20the%20company%20and%20the%20board%20of%20directors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECarlsten%20was%20previously%20CEO%20of%20the%20Danish%20Centre%20for%20AI%20Innovation.%20She%20also%20managed%20product%20portfolios%20at%20SandboxAQ%20and%20launched%20the%20quantum%20computing%20service%20at%20Amazon%20Web%20Services.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20nearly%20the%20entire%20company's%20staff%20gone%2C%20Carlsten%20is%20starting%20from%20scratch%2C%20except%20for%20the%20same%20BIRD%20ticker%20symbol%20that%20trades%20on%20the%20NASDAQ.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20spoke%20with%20Carlsten%20about%20her%20plans.%20This%20interview%20has%20been%20edited%20and%20condensed%20for%20clarity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBI%3A%20Did%20you%20ever%20imagine%20you%20would%20be%20working%20at%20Allbirds%2C%20and%20it%20would%20not%20be%20a%20shoe%20company%2C%20but%20an%20AI%20infrastructure%20play%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECarlsten%3A%20I've%20been%20around%20the%20block%20in%20Silicon%20Valley.%20It's%20not%20that%20unusual.%20Slack%20started%20as%20a%20game.%20Twitter%20started%20as%20a%20podcast.%20SpaceX%20started%20as%20a%20rocket%20company%20and%20is%20now%20doing%20AI%20infrastructure.%20So%20there's%20precedent%20for%20some%20of%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEverybody's%20trying%20to%20be%20in%20the%20AI%20infrastructure%20space.%20This%20is%20probably%20not%20the%20most%20typical%20way%20to%20get%20into%20it%2C%20but%20we%20have%20a%20really%20good%20plan%20and%20strategy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20few%20months%2C%20people%20won't%20even%20remember%20the%20shoes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBI%3A%20What%20does%20the%20company%20you're%20taking%20over%20look%20like%20at%20this%20stage%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECarlsten%3A%20The%20important%20thing%20to%20remember%20is%20that%20the%20shoe%20business%20has%20been%20sold%2C%20so%20anybody%20who%20was%20dedicated%20to%20the%20retail%20business%20is%20no%20longer%20part%20of%20the%20company.%20My%20first%20task%20is%20to%20hire%20the%20team.%20This%20is%20a%20brand-new%20company%20with%20brand-new%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBI%3A%20Why%20not%20just%20start%20a%20new%20company%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECarlsten%3A%20In%20many%20ways%2C%20it%20is%20like%20a%20startup.%20I'm%20going%20to%20be%20growing%20a%20team%2C%20developing%20a%20new%20business%20model%2C%20approaching%20customers%2C%20and%20growing%20a%20pipeline%20of%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20also%20some%20advantages%20to%20being%20a%20public%20company.%20One%20of%20them%20is%20access%20to%20capital.%20We%20have%20an%20easier%20time%20as%20we're%20looking%20at%20acquisitions%20and%20partnering%20with%20others%20in%20the%20industry.%20The%20liquidity%20makes%20it%20a%20lot%20easier%20to%20recruit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20AI%2C%20speed%20is%20key.%20So%20why%20would%20you%20want%20to%20do%20things%20more%20slowly%20if%20you%20can%20do%20it%20faster%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBI%3A%20You're%20also%20now%20running%20a%20public%20company%20from%20day%20one%2C%20which%20brings%20a%20lot%20of%20scrutiny.%20Are%20you%20worried%20about%20that%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECarlsten%3A%20AI%20fluctuates%2C%20whether%20it's%20public%20or%20private.%20This%20is%20a%20business%20that%20is%20never%20static.%20AI%20is%20moving%20incredibly%20fast.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECustomers%20are%20demanding%20things%20very%20differently%20than%20they%20were%20just%20a%20couple%20of%20months%20ago.%20So%20I%20don't%20think%20that%20makes%20much%20of%20a%20difference%20in%20how%20we%20will%20build%20the%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBI%3A%20What%20exactly%20is%20Smartbird%20going%20to%20do%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECarlsten%3A%20We%20are%20an%20AI%20infrastructure%20company%2C%20and%20what%20makes%20us%20different%20is%20that%20we%20are%20focusing%20on%20the%20mid-market%2C%20such%20as%20enterprises%20that%20are%20in%20the%20pharma%20space%20or%20financial%20services%20space%2C%20and%20also%20countries%20that%20are%20interested%20in%20sovereign%20AI%20or%20having%20regional%20AI%20infrastructure%20accessible%20to%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20of%20these%20players%20are%20doing%20more%20AI.%20They%20have%20more%20needs%20for%20persistent%20AI%20infrastructure%2C%20but%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%20for%20whatever%20reason%2C%20they%20cannot%20use%20or%20won't%20use%20the%20public%20clouds.%20They%20are%20very%20interested%20in%20making%20sure%20their%20proprietary%20data%20does%20not%20enter%20a%20shared%20multi-tenant%20infrastructure%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERight%20now%2C%20their%20choices%20are%20either%20shared%20infrastructure%20or%20building%20their%20own.%20And%20most%20of%20the%20people%20that%20I%20talk%20to%20in%20this%20space%20want%20to%20do%20more%20AI%2C%20but%20that%20doesn't%20mean%20that%20they%20want%20to%20build%20that%20AI%20infrastructure.%20Right%20now%2C%20they're%20doing%20it%20because%20they%20have%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBI%3A%20You're%20going%20up%20against%20Amazon%2C%20Google%2C%20CoreWeave%2C%20and%20a%20lot%20of%20other%20established%20players.%20How%20do%20you%20plan%20to%20compete%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECarlsten%3A%20We're%20not%20competing%20head-on%20with%20hyperscalers%20like%20AWS%20or%20Azure%20or%20even%20large%20neoclouds%20like%20CoreWeave.%20Those%20guys%20are%20very%20good%20at%20building%20massive-scale%20shared%20infrastructure%2C%20which%20is%20the%20opposite%20of%20what%20we%20want%20to%20be%20doing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20will%20focus%20on%20customers%20who%20need%20AI%20infrastructure%20at%20a%20smaller%20scale.%20Usually%2C%20they%20want%20single-tenant%20infrastructure%2C%20something%20that%20looks%20like%20a%20GPU%20cluster%20that%20they%20own%20and%20can%20fully%20control%20without%20having%20the%20disadvantages%20of%20managing%20the%20stack%20themselves.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBI%3A%20Where%20are%20you%20getting%20the%20GPUs%20from%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECarlsten%3A%20We'll%20be%20sourcing%20from%20multiple%20vendors.%20One%20of%20the%20things%20we'll%20be%20offering%20customers%20is%20the%20flexibility%20to%20build%20something%20specifically%20for%20their%20requirements.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBI%3A%20Are%20you%20going%20to%20buy%20the%20infrastructure%20or%20lease%20it%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECarlsten%3A%20We%20will%20purchase%20the%20infrastructure%20and%20build%20it%20out%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20customer.%20We're%20not%20building%20ahead%20of%20demand.%20We%20are%20building%20something%20for%20specific%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20can%20be%20a%20lot%20more%20agile%20than%20the%20bigger%20players.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcompany-formerly-known-as-allbirds-talks-about-its-ai-pivot-2026-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1781690401000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a30a18d9ab49a56117201c3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcompany-formerly-known-as-allbirds-talks-about-its-ai-pivot-2026-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Allbirds%20announced%20It%20would%20no%20longer%20sell%20shoes%20and%20instead%20become%20an%20AI%20infrastructure%20provider.%20Business%20Insider%20talked%20to%20the%20new%20CEO.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22bbergman%40insider.com%20(Ben%20Bergman)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22ChatGPT%20share%20falls%20below%2050%25%20for%20the%20first%20time%20ever%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1781690363000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-131795131%2Cimgsize-23600.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Ftechnology%2Ftech-news%2Fchatgpt-share-falls-below-50-for-the-first-time-ever-here-are-the-ai-chatbots-that-have-taken-away-share-from-sam-altmans-company%2Farticleshow%2F131795132.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22OpenAI's%20ChatGPT%20is%20no%20longer%20the%20dominant%20force%20in%20the%20AI%20assistant%20market.%20Competitors%20like%20Google's%20Gemini%20and%20Anthropic's%20Claude%20are%20gaining%20significant%20ground.%20This%20shift%20reflects%20a%20rapidly%20evolving%20landscape%20where%20users%20are%20increasingly%20engaging%20with%20multiple%20AI%20platforms.%20The%20overall%20AI%20app%20market%20is%20also%20experiencing%20substantial%20growth%20in%20downloads%20and%20user%20spending.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20TECH%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A99%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Lagaan'%20actor%20Paul%20Blackthorne%20recalls%20wild%20memory%20of%20jumping%20naked%20into%20the%20ocean%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1781690347000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-131794864%2Cimgsize-47114.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Flagaan-actor-paul-blackthornes-recalls-wild-memory-of-jumping-naked-into-the-ocean-while-shooting-in-bhuj-said-yes-to-work-with-the-incredible-aamir-khan%2Farticleshow%2F131794864.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F131794864.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ECelebrating%20'Lagaan's'%2025th%20anniversary%2C%20actor%20Paul%20Blackthorne%2C%20who%20played%20Captain%20Andrew%20Russell%2C%20shared%20his%20life-changing%20experience.%20He%20recalled%20Aamir%20Khan's%20vision%2C%20AR%20Rahman's%20impactful%20music%2C%20and%20a%20surreal%20beach%20encounter%20with%20flamingos%20and%20flying%20fish.%20Blackthorne%20remains%20touched%20by%20the%20enduring%20affection%20audiences%20still%20show%20for%20the%20iconic%20film.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22People%20don't%20trust%20AI.%20They%20do%20yearn%20for%20Lunchables%3A%20survey.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223744%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Lunchables%20snack%20is%20seen%20on%20a%20package.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a31bba42bbd1d834ef2458a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222496%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20cheesy%20bite%20of%20nostalgia%20can%20help%20soothe%20your%20AI%20jitters.%3Cp%3EIllustration%20by%20Justin%20Sullivan%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAs%20Americans%20use%20AI%20more%20they're%20trusting%20AI%20companies%20less%2C%20recent%20Morning%20Consult%20surveys%20show.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20the%20popularity%20of%20nostalgic%20products%20like%20Lunchables%20and%20Capri-Sun%20is%20rising.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20trend%20suggests%20consumers%20want%20the%20comfort%20of%20familiar%20brands%20in%20uncertain%20times.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20faster%20things%20change%2C%20the%20more%20we%20gravitate%20toward%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fretro-tech-comeback-razr-cds-kickback-sales-nostalgia-y2k-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethings%20that%20stay%20the%20same%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20no%20secret%20that%20AI%20is%20disrupting%20many%20aspects%20of%20modern%20life%2C%20but%20recent%20survey%20data%20shows%20that%20the%20more%20people%20use%20the%20tech%2C%20the%20less%20they%20trust%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20latest%20numbers%20from%20market%20research%20firm%20Morning%20Consult%2C%20released%20Tuesday%2C%20found%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsundar-pichai-google-graduation-speech-stanford-ai-backlash-eric-schmidt%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%20was%20one%20of%20the%20least%20trusted%3C%2Fa%3E%20categories%20among%20US%20consumers%2C%20with%20seven%20out%20of%2010%20major%20AI%20brands%20seeing%20year-over-year%20declines%20in%20their%20net%20trust%20scores.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EGoogle's%20Gemini%20managed%20to%20buck%20the%20trend%20and%20improve%20its%20score%20by%20six%20points%20to%20lead%20the%20pack%20with%20a%20net%20trust%20score%20of%2024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20some%20of%20the%20brands%20that%20saw%20the%20greatest%20improvement%20in%20consumer%20trust%20scores%20were%20decidedly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcapri-sun-selling-big-bottles-fans-silver-pouches-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elow-tech%20and%20high-nostalgia%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20Capri-Sun%2C%20Lunchables%2C%20Hot%20Wheels%2C%20and%20Mr.%20Pibb.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20unites%20them%20is%20that%20they%20belong%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-anxiety-pushing-gen-z-alpha-to-old-tech-analog-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Especific%20register%20of%20American%20memory%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20the%20brand%20landscape%20of%20childhood%2C%20before%20adult%20complexity%20set%20in%2C%26quot%3B%20Morning%20Consult%20said%20in%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20has%20tracked%20trust%20scores%20for%20nearly%20600%20brands%20since%202018%20and%20found%20that%20Americans'%20overall%20trust%20in%20consumer%20brands%20is%20higher%20than%20ever%20in%20spite%20of%2C%20well%2C%20%3Cem%3Eeverything%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20high-ranking%20brands%20%E2%80%94%20Dawn%20dish%20soap%2C%20Band-Aid%20wound%20care%2C%20Heinz%20ketchup%20%E2%80%94%20are%20%26quot%3Breliable%20if%20not%20particularly%20exciting%26quot%3B%20and%20have%20%26quot%3Beliminated%20surprise%20from%20the%20consumer%20relationship%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20also%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ehighlighted%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgap-is-back-mark-breitbard-global-brand-ceo-comeback-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGap's%20return%20to%20popularity%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20it%20attributed%20to%20a%20heavy%20adoption%20of%20Y2K%20aesthetics%2C%20harkening%20back%20to%20a%20comparatively%20less%20complicated%20(or%20at%20least%20slower-moving)%20era.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmericans'%20fondness%20for%20decades-old%20standbys%20stands%20in%20stark%20contrast%20to%20their%20feelings%20about%20AI%20companies%2C%20many%20of%20which%20are%20evolving%20with%20head-spinning%20speed%20and%20driving%20eye-watering%20financial%20valuations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20more%20detailed%20Morning%20Consult%20report%20on%20AI%20published%20in%20May%20found%20that%20more%20than%20a%20third%20of%20survey%20respondents%20do%20not%20trust%20AI%20%26quot%3Bat%20all%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20roughly%20matching%20the%20share%20of%20people%20who%20have%20a%20positive%20view%20of%20the%20tech.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmong%20ten%20of%20the%20leading%20companies%2C%20Meta%20AI%2C%20Perplexity%20AI%2C%20and%20xAI%20saw%20the%20sharpest%20declines%20in%20overall%20trust%20ratings%20since%20last%20year.%20One%20in%20five%20respondents%20agreed%20with%20the%20statement%20that%20AI%20companies'%20products%20present%20%26quot%3Ba%20real%20risk%26quot%3B%20of%20ending%20human%20civilization.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%202026%2C%20a%20significant%20portion%20of%20consumers%20are%20in%20anchoring%20mode%3A%20seeking%20brands%20they%20can%20count%20on%20when%20other%20parts%20of%20their%20environment%20feel%20unstable%2C%26quot%3B%20Morning%20Consult%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%