-volatile%E2%80%94%20retail%20stocks%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks%2Ftsla-stock%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETesla%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks%2Fnvda-stock%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENvidia%3C%2Fa%3E.%20No%20matter%20what%2C%20the%20bravest%20investors%20will%20find%20risk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20it's%20far%20too%20early%20to%20draw%20any%20overarching%20conclusions%20from%20the%20market's%20first%20day%20slinging%20Spacex%20options%2C%20it's%20still%20useful%20to%20monitor%20the%20activity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20some%20highlights%20from%20day%20one.%20All%20upside%20percentages%20were%20calculated%20from%20Tuesday's%20closing%20price%20of%20%24201.80.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%207%20most-traded%20options%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Col%3E%3Cli%3ECall%20option%20betting%20on%20SPCX%20to%20rise%209%25%20to%20%24220%20by%20June%2018%3A%2064%2C893%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ECall%20option%20betting%20on%20SPCX%20to%20rise%204%25%20to%20%24210%20by%20June%2018%3A%2063%2C425%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EPut%20option%20betting%20on%20SPCX%20to%20fall%201%25%20to%20%24200%20by%20June%2018%3A%2055%2C473%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ECall%20option%20betting%20on%20SPCX%20to%20rise%2024%25%20to%20%24250%20by%20June%2018%3A%2054%2C140%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ECall%20option%20betting%20on%20SPCX%20to%20rise%207%25%20to%20%24215%20by%20June%2018%3A%2046%2C199%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ECall%20option%20betting%20on%20SPCX%20to%20rise%2049%25%20to%20%24300%20by%20June%2018%3A%2041%2C146%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EPut%20option%20betting%20on%20SPCX%20to%20fall%2011%25%20to%20%24180%20by%20June%2018%3A%2038%2C866%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Fol%3E%3Cp%3E(Note%3A%20Options%20volume%20doesn't%20show%20whether%20contracts%20were%20bought%20or%20sold%2C%20making%20it%20impossible%20to%20determine%20overall%20bullish%20or%20bearish%20sentiment%20from%20volume%20alone.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20seven%20of%20the%20most-traded%20contracts%20expire%20Thursday.%20Some%20are%20tied%20to%20relatively%20modest%20moves%20in%20the%20stock%20over%20the%20next%20two%20days%2C%20while%20others%20would%20require%20a%20dramatic%20rally%20to%20pay%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOther%20odds%20and%20ends%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ESpaceX%20was%20the%20third-most-popular%20single%20stock%20in%20the%20options%20market%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20trailing%20just%20Tesla%20and%20Nvidia.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%2016th-most-traded%20options%20contract%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20most%20popular%20one%20not%20set%20to%20expire%20on%20Thursday%20%E2%80%94%20was%20a%20put%20option%20betting%20on%20SpaceX%20stock%20to%20hit%20%24205%20by%20Sept.%2018.%20This%20contract%2C%20which%20closed%20Tuesday%20in%20the%20money%2C%20is%20likely%20hedging%20activity%20around%20the%20first%20tranche%20of%20lock-up%20expiration%2C%20Susquehanna%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frecord-volume-spacex-stock-price-call-put-options-casino-open-2026-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1781689801000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a31bc254074dae0e2044669%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frecord-volume-spacex-stock-price-call-put-options-casino-open-2026-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20record-setting%20options%20debut%20suggests%20investors%20will%20trade%20SpaceX%20like%20other%20retail%20favorites%20Tesla%20and%20Nvidia.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jciolli%40businessinsider.com%20(Joe%20Ciolli)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A98%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Raveena%20was%20called%20'Little%20Mix%20Jinx'%20before%20'Mohra'%20with%20Akshay%20Kumar%20happened%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1781689399000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstati