0owner%20Sean%20McDonnell%20said%20he%20tries%20to%20remain%20prepared%20for%20unforeseen%20circumstances%20with%20using%20AI.%3Cp%3Edikushin%2FGetty%20Images%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EUK-based%20business%20owner%20Sean%20McDonnell%20relies%20on%20AI%20for%20his%20web%20design%20business%20and%20SaaS%20website.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-white-house-fable-mythos-5-drama-explained-2026-6%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EThe%20White%20House%20ordered%20Anthropic%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20cut%20foreign%20access%20to%20Fable%205%20while%20McDonell%20was%20mid-task.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EMcDonnell%20emphasizes%20importance%20of%20backup%20plans%20due%20to%20AI%20tool%20disruptions%20like%20the%20Fable%20incident.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Sean%20McDonnell%2C%2043%2C%20who%20lives%20in%20England.%20McDonnell%20is%20the%20founder%20of%20the%20web%20design%20company%20Kaizen%20and%20the%20SaaS%20website%20Consigns.%20The%20following%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDeveloping%20my%20website%20would%20not%20have%20been%20possible%20without%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20started%20my%20web%20design%20business%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%20which%20also%20led%20me%20to%20create%20a%20website%20that%20provides%20software%20to%20help%20companies%20track%20their%20waste.%20I%20run%20both%20of%20these%20ventures%20with%20my%20partner%2C%20and%20we%20enlist%20contractors%20for%20some%20operations%20and%20software%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe're%20a%20small%20team%2C%20and%20AI%20tools%20are%20a%20big%20help.%20Last%20week%2C%20I%20saw%20a%20few%20posts%20online%20showing%20the%20amazing%20things%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-claude-fable-5-mythos-class-model-release-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAnthropic's%20new%20Fable%20model%3C%2Fa%3E%20can%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20keen%20to%20try%20this%20new%20technology%2C%20but%20didn't%20get%20much%20of%20a%20chance%20to%20use%20it.%20A%20few%20hours%20in%2C%20I%20was%20mid-task%20when%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-white-house-ordered-export-controls-anthropic-mythos-fable-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethe%20US%20government%20forced%20Anthropic%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20cut%20off%20foreign%20access%20to%20Fable%20with%20little%20to%20no%20notice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Caside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20wants%20to%20talk%20to%20founders%20of%20AI-powered%20companies%20with%20fewer%20than%2010%20workers%2C%20and%20employees%20working%20alongside%20AI%20agents%2C%20to%20understand%20what%20the%20%26quot%3BTiny%20Teams%26quot%3B%20era%20really%20feels%20like%20%E2%80%94%20the%20wins%2C%20the%20fears%2C%20and%20the%20human%20skills%20that%20stand%20out.%20Share%20your%20story%20by%20filling%20out%20this%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLScO-Lptuw9eirYFmkAfOKc1aOvrFIW1jT2FzxuLJSexsTLExg%2Fviewform%3Fusp%3Dheader%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Equick%20form%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Faside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rug%20got%20pulled%20from%20under%20me%20pretty%20quickly%2C%20but%20because%20I%20was%20well-prepared%2C%20it%20didn't%20have%20a%20hugely%20disruptive%20impact%20on%20my%20business.%20It's%20a%20reminder%20that%20you%20can't%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-keep-brain-sharp-avoid-overreliance-ai-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Erely%20too%20heavily%20on%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20a%20founder%2C%20and%20you%20should%20always%20have%20a%20backup%20plan%20in%20case%20of%20unforeseen%20circumstances.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2268441fef-57ab-49bc-8e0f-184867418529%5C%22%3EI%20was%20keen%20to%20give%20Fable%20a%20try%2C%20but%20it%20was%20short-lived%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20like%20using%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-codex-elevated-errors-at-capacity-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EOpenAI's%20Codex%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20repetitive%2C%20code-intensive%20work%2C%20and%20Claude%20for%20tasks%20that%20help%20design%20the%20product's%20aesthetics.%20AI%20has%20been%20able%20to%20completely%20change%20the%20architecture%20of%20our%20codebase%20in%20a%20day%2C%20whereas%20a%20task%20like%20that%20would've%20taken%20a%20developer%20weeks%20to%20do%20manually.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20seeing%20so%20much%20about%20it%20online%2C%20I%20wanted%20to%20use%20Fable%20to%20conduct%20a%20full%20review%20of%20our%20product%20for%20safety%20and%20security%20flags.%20The%20model%20was%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20making%20some%20key%20changes%20to%20our%20codebase%20when%20it%20got%20shut%20off%20instantly%20with%20a%20notice%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-model-access-mistral-opportunity-ai-sovereignty-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EClaude%20Fable%205%20is%20currently%20unavailable%3C%2Fa%3E.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20didn't%20realize%20until%20the%20next%20day%20that%20this%20had%20happened%20because%20the%20US%20government%20ordered%20Anthropic%20to%20block%20foreign%20access%20to%20the%20model.%20It's%20been%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20bummer%2C%20and%20I%20feel%20bad%20for%20the%20people%20at%20Anthropic%20for%20making%20a%20brilliant%20product%20and%20having%20the%20rug%20pulled%20from%20under%20them%2C%20too.%20I'm%20also%20quite%20annoyed%20we%20didn't%20get%20to%20do%20more%20with%20Fable.%20I%20think%20it%20could've%20propelled%20us%20so%20much%20further.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227ad3b09e-20de-4dd3-9b33-42c87fb0964f%5C%22%3EBeing%20prepared%20helped%20us%20avoid%20a%20huge%20disruption%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20isn't%20the%20first%20time%20we've%20had%20issues%20with%20using%20Claude.%20In%20the%20past%2C%20when%20we%20used%20Opus%204.6%2C%20it%20would%20stop%20mid-task%20because%20it%20hit%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpylon-ceo-tokenmaxxing-era-coming-to-end-ai-spend-limits-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethe%20token%20limit%3C%2Fa%3E%20so%20quickly.%20We%20didn't%20realize%20how%20token-heavy%20the%20tool%20was%2C%20and%20it%20left%20our%20codebase%20in%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20mess.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20we'd%20learned%20this%20lesson%20with%204.6%2C%20we%20made%20sure%20we%20were%20more%20prepared%20for%20unforeseen%20circumstances%20with%20using%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20we%20started%20our%20product%20review%20last%20week%2C%20I%20asked%20Fable%20to%20create%20a%20guide%20that%20both%20Claude%20or%20other%20AI%20models%20could%20follow.%20This%20enabled%20us%20to%20pass%20the%20remaining%20tasks%20to%20other%20agents%20when%20we%20lost%20access%20to%20Fable.%20We%20passed%20some%20to%20Codex%20and%20others%20to%20Claude%204.8.%20If%20we%20hadn't%20been%20prepared%20this%20way%2C%20the%20Fable%20issue%20could've%20resulted%20in%20lots%20of%20work%20being%20out%20the%20window.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFable%20getting%20pulled%20didn't%20have%20a%20major%20impact%20because%20we%20were%20ready%20for%20it%2C%20but%20it%20ruined%20our%20momentum.%20We're%20working%20on%20a%20deadline%2C%20and%20every%20minute%20counts%2C%20so%20delays%20like%20this%20can%20be%20quite%20disruptive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f5737e02-ea57-4ed2-b40c-aa42740174f4%5C%22%3EAlways%20have%20a%20plan%20B%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20Anthropic%20incident%20has%20solidified%20my%20conviction%20that%20you%20can't%20depend%20completely%20on%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20government%20were%20to%20shut%20off%20AI%20access%20completely%2C%20our%20business%20wouldn't%20end%2C%20because%20we've%20already%20built%20out%20our%20platform%2C%20but%20we%20are%20quite%20dependent%20on%20AI.%20A%20situation%20like%20that%20would%20likely%20increase%20our%20costs%2C%20partly%20because%20we'd%20have%20to%20switch%20to%20the%20old-school%20method%20of%20hiring%20developers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20today's%20AI%20era%2C%20it's%20important%20to%20always%20have%20a%20plan%20B.%20Don't%20just%20rely%20on%20one%20AI%20tool.%20It's%20good%20to%20understand%20the%20strengths%20of%20different%20models.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMake%20sure%20you're%20documenting%20things%20as%20you%20go%20by%20keeping%20records%20that%20exist%20outside%20your%20AI%20tool.%20If%20Claude%20knows%20all%20about%20our%20code%20base%2C%20but%20it%20gets%20pulled%20tomorrow%2C%20would%20I%20be%20able%20to%20give%20that%20over%20to%20a%20developer%3F%20At%20this%20stage%2C%20I%20think%20I%20could%2C%20because%20I've%20been%20documenting%20everything%20as%20I%20go.%20It's%20a%20fail-safe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EA%20spokesperson%20from%20The%20White%20House%20told%20Business%20Insider%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20Trump%20administration%20is%20collaborating%20with%20AI%20industry%20leaders%20to%20balance%20cutting-edge%20innovation%20with%20national%20security%20concerns%20that%20affect%20both%20the%20United%20States%20and%20our%20allies.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAnthropic%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20you%20have%20a%20similar%20story%20to%20share%3F%20If%20so%2C%20you%20can%20reach%20out%20to%20one%20of%20the%20reporters%20at%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aaapplegate%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Eaapplegate%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20and%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Accheong%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Eccheong%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3E.%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fusing-anthropics-fable-when-foreign-access-disappeared-mid-project-2026-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1781687461000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a31bc132bbd1d834ef24593%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fusing-anthropics-fable-when-foreign-access-disappeared-mid-project-2026-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20UK%20founder%20was%20mid%20project%20with%20Anthropic's%20Fable%205%20model%20when%20a%20US%20government%20order%20halted%20foreign%20access.%20Luckily%2C%20he%20had%20a%20backup%20plan.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ccheong%40insider.com%20(Charissa%20Cheong%2CAgnes%20Applegate)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A98%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BWe%20Are%20Always%20Ready%26quot%3B%3A%20PM%20Modi%20As%20He%20Stands%20Beside%20Trump%20For%20G7%20Summit%20Photo%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22Trump%20and%20Modi's%20meeting%20marks%20their%20first%20face-to-face%20interaction%20in%20around%2016%20months.%22%2C%22published%22%3A1781687347000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpm-modi-stands-next-to-trump-at-g7-summit-family-photo-says-we-are-always-ready-11647755%23publisher%3Dnewsstand%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Trump%20and%20Modi's%20meeting%20marks%20their%20first%20face-to-face%20interaction%20in%20around%2016%20months.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A99%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpm-modi-stands-next-to-trump-at-g7-summit-family-photo-says-we-are-always-ready-11647755%23publisher%3Dnewsstand%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%223%20things%20for%20investors%20to%20watch%20for%20during%20Kevin%20Warsh's%20first%20presser%20as%20Fed%20Chair%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225548%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kevin%20Warsh%20and%20Trump%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a316e0c73f469f2923c65b6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223698%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFederal%20Reserve%20Chair%20Kevin%20Warsh%20and%20US%20President%20Donald%20Trump%3Cp%3ERoberto%20Schmidt%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EKevin%20Warsh%20will%20lead%20his%20first%20press%20conference%20as%20chair%20of%20the%20Federal%20Reserve%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20market%20is%20nearly%20unanimous%20that%20the%20Fed%20will%20hold%20rates%20steady.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EInvestors%20look%20for%20what's%20to%20come%20within%20the%20dot%20plot%20and%20Warsh's%20tone%20as%20stock%20trade%20near%20highs.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EKevin%20Warsh%20will%20take%20to%20the%20podium%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffed-meeting-kevin-warsh-interest-rates-what-to-expect-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edeliver%20his%20first%20remarks%20as%20Federal%20Reserve%20chair%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInvestors%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cmegroup.com%2Fmarkets%2Finterest-rates%2Fcme-fedwatch-tool.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enearly%20unanimously%20expecting%20the%20Fed%20to%20hold%20rates%20steady%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20shifting%20the%20focus%20to%20other%20signals%20coming%20out%20of%20the%20meeting%20of%20what's%20next%20for%20the%20US%20central%20bank.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWarsh%20succeeded%20Jerome%20Powell%2C%20who%20is%20now%20a%20Fed%20governor.%20He%20was%20initially%20seen%20as%20more%20dovish%20than%20his%20predecessor%2C%20since%20Trump%20nominated%20him%2C%20but%20there%20are%20some%20hawkish%20expectations%20heading%20into%20Wednesday.%20The%20press%20conference%20marks%20the%20new%20Fed%20chair's%20chance%20to%20set%20expectations%20under%20his%20leadership.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeyond%20the%20rate%20decision%20itself%2C%20here%20are%20three%20things%20that%20investors%20are%20keeping%20an%20eye%20on%20during%20the%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22591f97d6-3d91-4673-acb1-014ea3487133%5C%22%3E1.%20A%20fresh%20dot%20plot%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EInvestors%20will%20get%20a%20look%20at%20where%20FOMC%20see%20rates%20heading%20going%20forward%20as%20well%20as%20an%20assessment%20of%20how%20divided%20the%20members'%20outlooks%20are.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Fed%20will%20release%20its%20Summary%20of%20Economic%20Projections%20which%20includes%20the%20dot%20plot.%20Each%20dot%20represents%20a%20FOMC%20member's%20outlook%20for%20rates%20in%202026%20and%20beyond.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20has%20the%20potential%20to%20be%20even%20more%20impactful%20than%20normal%20given%20the%20change%20in%20leadership%2C%20the%20change%20in%20composition%20in%20the%20FOMC%20and%20inflation%20that%20is%20stubbornly%20above%20target%2C%26quot%3B%20Daniel%20Murray%20deputy%20CIO%20and%20global%20head%20of%20research%20at%20EFGAM%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.efginternational.com%2Fus%2Finsights%2F2026%2Ffed_preview_testing_times_for_the_new_fed_chair.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20dot-plot%20could%20be%20one%20official%20short%20with%20Bank%20of%20America%20signaling%20they%20don't%20expect%20Warsh%20to%20partake.%20Previously%20he%20has%20said%20he%20wants%20to%20do%20away%20with%20the%20Fed%20providing%20forward%20looking%20guidance%20like%20the%20dot-plot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInvestors%20went%20from%20pricing%20in%20two%20to%20three%20rate%20cuts%20in%202026%20to%20weighing%20potential%20rate%20hikes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2277435b01-7e39-461e-bb24-40229b582fad%5C%22%3E2.%20Warsh's%20tone%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20market%20is%20broadly%20in%20agreement%20that%20the%20Fed%20will%20hold%20rates%20steady%2C%20the%20question%20becomes%20will%20it%20be%20a%20dovish%20hold%20or%20a%20hawkish%20hold.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBank%20of%20America%20surveys%20found%20that%20most%20(55%25)%20fund%20managers%20expect%20a%20hawkish%20hold%20while%20a%20third%20expect%20a%20dovish%20hold.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20Fed%20chair's%20commentary%20and%20tone%20will%20be%20a%20critical%20part%20of%20the%20meeting%20for%20investors%20assessing%20what's%20next%20for%20the%20Fed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHistorically%2C%20Warsh%20has%20been%20a%20hawk%20and%20he%20did%20come%20off%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffed-chair-kevin-warsh-hearing-takeaways-wall-street-trump-powell-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emore%20hawkish%3C%2Fa%3E%20than%20many%20expected%20in%20his%20confirmation%20hearing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInteractive%20Brokers%20senior%20economist%20Jos%C3%A9%20Torres%20flagged%20that%20the%20US-Iran%20deal%20helps%20Warsh%20with%20optics%20heading%20into%20to%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20sharp%20drop%20in%20energy%20costs%20immediately%20prior%20to%20the%20inaugural%20Warsh-led%20FOMC%20offers%20favorable%20first-impression%20dynamics%20and%20raises%20the%20likelihood%20of%20an%20increasingly%20patient%20central%20bank%20willing%20to%20look%20through%20the%20current%20short-term%20inflation%20as%20a%20one-time%20shock%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22daaba2f8-f181-44fb-93dd-54c9ce833e50%5C%22%3E3.%20Impact%20on%20asset%20prices%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EStocks%20are%20near%20record%20highs%20after%20earnings%20strength%20more%20than%20offset%20the%20Iran%20war%20drawdown.%20The%20recent%20relief%20rally%20has%20carried%20equities%20further.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20June%20meeting%20comes%20in%20the%20lull%20between%20the%20first%20and%20second%20quarter%20earnings%20seasons%20when%20the%20market%20has%20less%20data%20points%20in%20the%20form%20of%20corporate%20reports%20to%20digest.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDepending%20on%20the%20tone%20and%20how%20much%20this%20meeting%20reshapes%20investor%20expectations%2C%20it%20could%20dictate%20the%20market's%20narrative%20for%20the%20next%20several%20weeks%2C%20at%20least%20until%20earnings%20season%20takes%20over%2C%26quot%3B%20eToro%20US%20investment%20analyst%2C%20Bret%20Kenwell%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKenwell%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BWarsh%20takes%20over%20with%20stocks%20hovering%20near%20record%20highs%20and%20the%20labor%20market%20still%20looking%20solid%2C%20but%20with%20inflation%20reaccelerating.%20Investors%20are%20trying%20to%20figure%20out%20whether%20the%20new%20Fed%20chair%20will%20use%20his%20first%20major%20moment%20to%20reset%20expectations.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffed-rates-interest-yield-kevin-warsh-trump-federal-reserve-chair-2026-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1781687101000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a318ff8564c774507cd30ce%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffed-rates-interest-yield-kevin-warsh-trump-federal-reserve-chair-2026-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20market%20is%20nearly%20unanimous%20that%20the%20Fed%20will%20hold%20rates%20steady.%20But%20Warsh%20could%20move%20the%20market%20depending%20on%20what%20he%20says%20about%20rates.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22nbuchanan%40insider.com%20(Naomi%20Buchanan)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rainbow%20warned%20its%20models%20that%20AI%20meant%20fewer%20jobs.%20Then%20their%20doppelg%C3%A4ngers%20appeared.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Photo%20collage%20Featuring%20images%20from%20a%20lawsuit%20toward%20the%20brand%20Rainbow%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a2c67e450aa6577af872470%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20retailer%20Rainbow%20warned%20its%20fashion%20models%20that%20%26quot%3Bfewer%20people%20will%20be%20needed%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20and%20to%20expect%20a%20%26quot%3Bhuge%20increase%20in%20A.I.%20use.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20New%20York%20State%20Unified%20Court%20System%3B%20Tyler%20Le%2FBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20June%2C%20fashion%20models%20for%20the%20fashion%20retailer%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ERainbow%20received%20a%20warning%3A%20AI%20was%20ramping%20up%2C%20and%20the%20number%20of%20workers%20needed%20would%20be%20ramping%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20may%20have%20already%20seen%20some%20changes%20taking%20place%20both%20within%20the%20studio%20and%20on%20the%20site%2C%26quot%3B%20wrote%20Rainbow's%20studio%20manager%2C%20Phil%20Caraway.%20The%20company%20had%20started%20%26quot%3Bstyling%20certain%20products%2C%20and%20generating%20avatars%2C%20with%20the%20assistance%20of%20A.I%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20explained%2C%20and%20while%20he%20couldn't%20say%20for%20certain%20whether%20any%20freelancers%20would%20lose%20their%20jobs%2C%20he%20wanted%20them%20to%20%26quot%3Bplan%20accordingly.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFewer%20people%20will%20be%20needed%20in%20the%20long%20term%2C%26quot%3B%20Caraway%20wrote%20in%20the%20previously%20unreported%20email.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20very%20likely%20that%20this%20Fall%20will%20see%20a%20huge%20increase%20in%20A.I.%20use.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThus%20began%20what%20several%20models%20described%20as%20a%20year%20of%20anxiety%20and%2C%20later%2C%20anger.%20They%20could%20see%20the%20company%20using%20AI%20to%20create%20synthetic%20models%20within%20view%20of%20where%20they%20worked%2C%20the%20models%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20the%20models'%20days%20in%20the%20New%20York%20office%20began%20to%20dwindle%2C%20they%20said%2C%20leaving%20many%20without%20work.%20Nearly%20a%20year%20after%20that%20June%20email%2C%20Rainbow%20has%20begun%20rehiring%20some%20models%20%E2%80%94%20though%20many%20remain%20out%20of%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20March%20of%20this%20year%2C%20the%20models%20began%20noticing%20Rainbow%20marketing%20images%20that%20looked%20like%20them%2C%20but%20posed%20in%20positions%20or%20locations%20that%20differed%20from%20the%20photo%20shoots%20they%20had%20participated%20in.%20Many%20suspected%20the%20doppelg%C3%A4ngers%20were%20the%20result%20of%20AI.%20The%20lookalike%20models%20cropped%20up%20across%20Rainbow's%20site%2C%20social%20media%2C%20and%20newsletters.%20A%20flurry%20of%20emails%20to%20Rainbow%20followed%2C%20along%20with%20a%20lawsuit%20by%20one%20model.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20AI%20technologies%20improve%2C%20workplaces%20across%20the%20country%20are%20experimenting%20with%20how%20to%20use%20them%20%E2%80%94%20and%20navigating%20the%20thorny%20question%20of%20their%20impact%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-job-impact-losses-shifting-sam-altman-mustafa-suleyman-comments-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eon%20human%20jobs%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Creative%20industries%20like%20modeling%20are%20especially%20exposed%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-influencers-aitana-lopez-sienna-rose-human-content-creators-fight-back-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAI-generated%20photos%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20videos%20improve%20in%20quality.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20is%20growing%20more%20common%20within%20the%20fashion%20industry.%20In%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ilr.cornell.edu%2Fworker-institute%2Fblog%2Fpublications%2Ffashions-data-doubles-how-ai-reshaping-modeling-work%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E2025%20study%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20Worker%20Institute%20at%20Cornell%20University%20ILR%20School%20and%20Data%20%26amp%3B%20Society%20in%20partnership%20with%20the%20Model%20Alliance%2C%20researchers%20said%20that%20e-commerce%20gigs%20were%20%26quot%3Bmore%20vulnerable%20to%20displacement%20by%20AI%20technologies.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Francheska%20Pujols%20is%20pictured%20modeling%20a%20Rainbow%20outfit%20on%20the%20left.%20Pujols%20said%20in%20a%20lawsuit%20that%20the%20image%20on%20the%20right%20looks%20like%20her%2C%20but%20she%20didn't%20pose%20this%20way%2C%20alleging%20Rainbow%20used%20AI.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a2c656024b3540ad29c2d55%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERainbow%20model%20Francheska%20Pujols%20modeled%20the%20skirt%20on%20the%20left.%20In%20a%20lawsuit%2C%20she%20said%20she%20didn't%20pose%20for%20the%20image%20on%20the%20right%2C%20though%20it%20resembles%20her.%3Cp%3ENew%20York%20State%20Unified%20Court%20System%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20spoke%20to%20multiple%20Rainbow%20employees%20and%20contractors%2C%20all%20of%20whom%20requested%20anonymity%2C%20and%20also%20reviewed%20dozens%20of%20email%20exchanges%20and%20images%2C%20as%20well%20as%20modeling%20contracts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRainbow%20is%20responsibly%20evaluating%20emerging%20AI%20technologies%20in%20the%20marketplace%2C%20and%20has%20and%20is%20committed%20to%20doing%20so%20in%20a%20proper%20manner%2C%26quot%3B%20David%20Cost%2C%20Rainbow's%20chief%20digital%20officer%2C%20wrote%20in%20a%20statement%20to%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20follow-up%20email%2C%20Cost%20wrote%20that%20%26quot%3BRainbow's%20dealings%20with%20its%20employees%20and%20independent%20contractors%20are%20private%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20the%20company%20disagreed%20with%20%26quot%3Bmuch%20of%20the%20purported%20'facts.'%26quot%3B%20He%20declined%20to%20comment%20on%20specific%20questions%20sent%20by%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BRainbow%20has%20acted%20appropriately%20and%20in%20accordance%20with%20its%20commitments%2C%20including%20contracts%20signed%20by%20models%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20how%20Rainbow's%20AI%20model%20experiment%20got%20messy%2C%20according%20to%20its%20workers%20%E2%80%94%20from%20a%20slowdown%20on%20human%20modeling%20work%20to%20contract%20disputes%20and%20hiring%20some%20of%20the%20models%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERainbow%2C%20founded%20in%20Brooklyn%20over%2090%20years%20ago%2C%20has%20over%20800%20stores%20nationwide%20and%20is%20privately%20owned.%20The%20retailer%20caters%20to%20thrifty%20consumers%20with%20steep%20discounts%2C%20similar%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffashion-nova-richard-saghianbillionaire-biggest-modern-home-one-2022-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFashion%20Nova%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20PrettyLittleThing.%20It%20also%20operates%20the%20similar%20brand%20KissDon'tTell.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20its%20e-commerce%20shoots%2C%20the%20Rainbow%20team%20looked%20for%20models%20without%20agency%20connections%2C%20one%20former%20stylist%20who%20helped%20recruit%20models%20said.%20Two%20models%20said%20that%20they%20were%20found%20on%20Instagram%20and%20had%20little%20paid%20modeling%20experience.%20Fees%20varied%20by%20model%2C%20though%20many%20said%20they%20made%20around%20%2450%20an%20hour.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThree%20models%20said%20that%20one%20Rainbow%20employee%20told%20them%20to%20be%20available%20for%20five%20days%20of%20work%20a%20week.%20The%20former%20stylist%20said%20that%20Rainbow%20asked%20its%20freelancers%20to%20be%20available%20Monday%20through%20Friday%2C%20but%20that%20it%20wasn't%20written%20into%20their%20contracts.%20Two%20models%20said%20they%20left%20their%20prior%20jobs%20for%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPartway%20through%202025%2C%20the%20models%20began%20to%20notice%20something%20different%20in%20the%20studio%3A%20AI%20training.%20Employees%20would%20lay%20out%20the%20clothes%20on%20a%20flat%20board%2C%20take%20photos%2C%20and%20upload%20them%20to%20an%20AI%20program%20called%20Lica%2C%20one%20employee%20said.%20Lica%20generated%20fully%20synthetic%20AI%20models%20%E2%80%94%20not%20duplicates%20of%20human%20models%20%E2%80%94%20for%20Rainbow%2C%20the%20employee%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20AI%20training%20caused%20significant%20anxiety%20among%20the%20models%2C%20they%20said.%20Trying%20to%20lighten%20the%20mood%2C%20some%20models%20said%20they%20would%20crack%20dark%20jokes%20about%20the%20system%20replacing%20them.%20Two%20models%20said%20that%20they%20recalled%20instances%20where%20the%20fit%20of%20a%20garment%20on%20their%20body%20was%20compared%20to%20an%20AI%20avatar%2C%20pointing%20out%20where%20the%20avatar%20needed%20to%20be%20more%20realistic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20Carraway's%20June%20email%20a%20year%20ago%2C%20the%20models%20braced%20for%20their%20work%20to%20drop%20off.%20For%20months%2C%20several%20models%20said%20that%20they%20continued%20to%20get%20consistent%20bookings.%20Then%2C%20they%20slowed%20down%2C%20the%20models%20said%2C%20and%20by%20mid-March%20of%20this%20year%2C%20the%20work%20dried%20up.%20Some%20models%20submitted%20their%20availability%20but%20said%20they%20received%20no%20response.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20that%20period%2C%20two%20Rainbow%20employees%20who%20are%20not%20models%20said%20that%20they%20went%20weeks%20without%20seeing%20any%20human%20models%20in%20the%20studio.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20models%20started%20spotting%20their%20doppelg%C3%A4ngers%20on%20Rainbow's%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20models%20had%20previously%20participated%20in%20product%20shots%20wearing%20Rainbow%20apparel%2C%20such%20as%20a%20long%20floral%20dress%2C%20while%20photographed%20in%20front%20of%20plain%20backgrounds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20doppelg%C3%A4ngers%20they%20later%20noticed%20looked%20strikingly%20similar%20%E2%80%94%20the%20same%20builds%2C%20facial%20features%2C%20and%20outfits%20they%20had%20worn%20%E2%80%94%20but%20were%20pictured%20with%20their%20bodies%20in%20entirely%20different%20positions.%20The%20models%20texted%20these%20images%20back%20and%20forth%20in%20a%20group%20chat.%20Business%20Insider%20viewed%20over%20a%20dozen%20such%20images.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20clause%20of%20the%20contracts%20many%20of%20the%20models%20had%20signed%20allowed%20Rainbow%20to%20use%20their%20images%20%26quot%3Bwhether%20intact%20or%20in%20part%2C%20composite%20or%20distorted%20in%20character%20or%20form%2C%20cropped%20or%20altered%2C%20without%20restrictions%20as%20to%20changes%20or%20transformations.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22On%20the%20left%2C%20a%20Rainbow%20model%20is%20pictured%20in%20an%20e-commerce%20shot.%20Francheska%20Pujols%20said%20in%20a%20lawsuit%20that%20she%20never%20shot%20in%20the%20location%20on%20the%20right.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a2ffa0f9ab49a561171fae2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20image%20on%20the%20left%20is%20from%20a%20Rainbow%20product%20page.%20In%20a%20lawsuit%20against%20the%20company%2C%20model%20Francheska%20Pujols%20said%20the%20models%20never%20posed%20for%20the%20image%20on%20the%20right.%3Cp%3EScreenshots%20via%20Rainbow%20(Site%3B%20Facebook)%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20image%20that%20sparked%20conversation%20in%20the%20group%20chat%20showed%20what%20the%20models%20suspected%20was%20an%20AI%20lookalike%20that%20altered%20the%20model's%20original%20skin%20tone.%20The%20model%20and%20the%20suspected%20AI%20lookalike%20had%20some%20similarities%20%E2%80%94%20the%20hairstyle%20and%20placement%20of%20the%20hair%20part%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20accessories%20and%20shoes%20%E2%80%94%20but%20also%20some%20differences%2C%20such%20as%20the%20nose%20shape.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENone%20of%20the%20employees%20Business%20Insider%20spoke%20to%20had%20directly%20seen%20the%20creation%20or%20editing%20of%20these%20doppelg%C3%A4ngers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20model%20for%20Rainbow%20is%20pictured%20on%20the%20left.%20Some%20models%20believe%20the%20one%20on%20the%20right%20is%20her%20AI%20lookalike%20with%20her%20skin%20darkened.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a2c62c224b3540ad29c2d34%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOn%20the%20left%2C%20a%20Rainbow%20model%20is%20pictured.%20Some%20models%20discussed%20whether%20the%20figure%20on%20the%20right%20was%20an%20AI%20lookalike%20with%20darkened%20skin%20tone.%20Neither%20was%20referenced%20in%20Pujols'%20lawsuit.%3Cp%3EScreenshots%20via%20Rainbow%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESeveral%20of%20the%20models%20who%20suspected%20that%20Rainbow%20was%20modifying%20their%20likenesses%20with%20AI%20raised%20issues%20with%20the%20company%20via%20email.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20models%2C%20Francheska%20Pujols%2C%20sued%20Rainbow%20on%20May%2022%2C%20alleging%20the%20images%20defamed%20her%20and%20caused%20confusion%20over%20her%20endorsement%20of%20the%20company's%20products%2C%20among%20other%20allegations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPujols%20wrote%20in%20an%20affidavit%20that%20her%20contract%20only%20covered%20images%20captured%20in%20photo%20shoots%2C%20and%20%26quot%3Bdoes%20not%20in%20any%20way%20authorize%20the%20creation%20of%20entirely%20new%20images%2C%20scenes%2C%20poses%2C%20or%20compositions%20that%20did%20not%20exist%20in%20the%20original%20content.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERainbow%20posted%20photos%20of%20what%20Pujols%20said%20is%20her%20AI%20doppelg%C3%A4nger%3B%20in%20one%2C%20she%20straddles%20a%20barstool.%20Another%20shows%20her%20seated%2C%20wearing%20a%20short%20skirt%2C%20with%20one%20leg%20raised.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPujols%20wrote%20to%20Business%20Insider%20that%20she%20would%20%26quot%3Bnever%20pose%20with%20my%20legs%20open%20or%20position%20myself%20in%20a%20sexualized%20manner%20for%20the%20world%20to%20see.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20extremely%20emotional%20and%20have%20many%20sleepless%20nights%20with%20the%20thought%20of%20the%20altered%20images%20of%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20Pujols%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BI%20sought%20a%20professional%20aide%20to%20help%20with%20sleep%20and%20reconciliation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Rainbow%20model%20Francheska%20Pujols%20said%20that%20both%20of%20these%20images%20look%20like%20her%2C%20but%20that%20she%20didn't%20take%20these%20shots.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a2c639f24b3540ad29c2d3f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPujols%20said%20in%20her%20lawsuit%20that%20both%20of%20these%20photos%20looked%20like%20her%2C%20but%20that%20she%20was%20never%20photographed%20in%20these%20poses.%3Cp%3ENew%20York%20State%20Unified%20Court%20System%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EPujols%20withdrew%20her%20suit%20on%20May%2029%20to%20pursue%20a%20private%20settlement%2C%20her%20attorney%20wrote%20in%20an%20affidavit.%20She%20refiled%20the%20lawsuit%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20Rainbow%20has%20stated%20previously%20in%20relation%20to%20this%20matter%2C%20Ms.%20Pujols'%20images%20were%20used%20properly%20and%20in%20accordance%20with%20the%20agreement%20she%20signed%2C%26quot%3B%20Joan%20McGillycuddy%2C%20Rainbow's%20chief%20legal%20officer%2C%20wrote%20in%20a%20statement%20to%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BThere%20is%20no%20violation%20of%20her%20rights.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERainbow's%20contracts%20said%20the%20models%20would%20receive%20double%20their%20day%20rate%20for%20image%20use%20outside%20that%20second%20clause.%20Some%20models%20requested%20compensation%20for%20the%20suspected%20AI%20images%20but%20were%20turned%20down%2C%20according%20to%20their%20messages%2C%20which%20were%20viewed%20by%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Rainbow%20model%20is%20pictured%20in%20an%20e-commerce%20shot%20on%20the%20left.%20The%20photo%20on%20the%20right%20shows%20a%20similar%20looking%20model%2C%20but%20in%20a%20different%20position%20and%20location.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a30759da4629406118999c5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOn%20the%20left%2C%20an%20image%20on%20Rainbow's%20product%20page.%20The%20right%20image%20shows%20what%20appears%20to%20be%20the%20same%20model%20in%20a%20different%20location%20and%20position.%20These%20were%20not%20in%20Pujols'%20lawsuit.%3Cp%3EScreenshots%20via%20Rainbow%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20the%20contract%20back-and-forth%20began.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20March%2010%2C%20amid%20the%20work%20slowdown%2C%20Caraway%20sent%20an%20email%20to%20the%20models.%20%26quot%3BTo%20account%20for%20today's%20rapidly-changing%20technology%20and%20expectations%20of%20use%2C%20Rainbow%20has%20come%20up%20with%20an%20updated%20Model%20Release%2C%26quot%3B%20Caraway%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20clause%20in%20the%20new%20contract%20was%20particularly%20controversial%20%E2%80%94%20one%20that%20the%20models%20interpreted%20as%20granting%20Rainbow%20sweeping%20AI%20rights.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20clause%20allowed%20Rainbow%20to%20use%20%26quot%3Bvarious%20technologies%2C%20tools%2C%20or%20production%20methods%20now%20known%20or%20later%20developed%2C%20including%20automated%20or%20computer-assisted%20techniques.%26quot%3B%20The%20clause%20should%20be%20interpreted%20%26quot%3Bbroadly%26quot%3B%20as%20long%20as%20the%20company%20was%20not%20%26quot%3Bmaterially%20misrepresenting%20the%20model%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20contract%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20the%20models%20said%20they%20refused%20to%20sign%20it.%20On%20March%2028%2C%20Carraway%20emailed%20the%20models%20that%20Rainbow%20agreed%20to%20remove%20a%20non-compete%20clause%2C%20but%20the%20technology%20usage%20clause%20was%20presented%20as%20a%20dealbreaker.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRainbow%20cannot%20adjust%20the%20AI%20clause%2C%26quot%3B%20Caraway%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BIn%20order%20to%20continue%20to%20be%20hired%2C%20this%20must%20be%20agreed%20to.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20clear%20if%20the%20contract%20negotiations%20contributed%20to%20or%20prolonged%20the%20work%20slowdown.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECost%2C%20Rainbow's%20CDO%2C%20hyped%20up%20the%20AI%20program%20Lica%20in%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fposts%2Fpriyaak_david-cost-chief-digital-officer-rainbow-ugcPost-7440099722314543104-bBtA%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EApril%20video%3C%2Fa%3E%20reposted%20by%20the%20startup's%20cofounder.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20amazing%20what%20the%20people%20at%20Lica%20have%20been%20able%20to%20do%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe're%20using%20them%20for%20product%20photography.%20We're%20also%20using%20them%20for%20editorial%20or%20things%20that%20you'd%20see%20on%20a%20homepage%20or%20in%20an%20email.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETwo%20staffers%20said%20the%20tool%20was%20buggy.%20Some%20of%20the%20synthetic%20models'%20legs%20were%20too%20short%2C%20one%20said%3B%20the%20AI%20repeatedly%20generated%20one%20synthetic%20model%20with%20a%20white%20cardigan%20over%20her%20clothes.%20Creating%20an%20AI%20image%20would%20also%20take%20long%20stretches%20of%20re-prompting%2C%20they%20said%2C%20often%20around%2015-30%20minutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERainbow%20is%20no%20longer%20using%20Lica%2C%20one%20staffer%20said.%20Lica%20told%20Business%20Insider%20in%20a%20statement%20that%20it%20is%20%26quot%3Bfocused%20on%20foundational%20AI%20research%20for%20multimodal%20design%20models.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20part%20of%20our%20research%20efforts%2C%20we%20provided%20interested%20enterprise%20partners%20with%20early%20access%20to%20emerging%20AI%20capabilities%20and%20model%20technologies%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20Lica%20representative%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BWe%20do%20not%20direct%2C%20supervise%2C%20or%20control%20our%20customers'%20implementation%20decisions%2C%20and%20we%20do%20not%20publicly%20comment%20on%20specific%20customer%20use%20cases.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERainbow%20began%20bringing%20some%20of%20its%20human%20models%20back%20at%20the%20end%20of%20April%2C%20employees%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20time%20around%2C%20some%20of%20the%20models%20received%20an%20agreement%20with%20the%20following%20clause%3A%20%26quot%3BCompany%20will%20not%20create%20digital%20replicas%2C%20train%20AI%20on%20Model%20likeness%2C%20or%20generate%20synthetic%20images%20not%20based%20on%20original%20Content.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERainbow%20is%20still%20producing%20images%20of%20the%20AI%20avatars%2C%20one%20staffer%20said%2C%20but%20not%20with%20Lica.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECost%2C%20the%20company's%20chief%20digital%20officer%2C%20referenced%20the%20state%20of%20AI%20experimentation%20at%20Rainbow%20in%20his%20LinkedIn%20job%20description.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEvery%20experiment%20designed%20to%20replace%20a%20person%20with%20AI%20failed%2C%26quot%3B%20Cost%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BEvery%20experiment%20designed%20to%20give%20a%20talented%20person%20more%20capability%20won%2C%20and%20won%20bigger%20than%20expected.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frainbow-shops-fashion-models-ai-use-jobs-impact-2026-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1781686801000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a2c681750aa6577af872477%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frainbow-shops-fashion-models-ai-use-jobs-impact-2026-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%2090-year-old%20retailer%20Rainbow%20told%20its%20fashion%20models%20%26quot%3Bfewer%20people%20will%20be%20needed%26quot%3B%20due%20to%20AI.%20The%20models%20say%20their%20likeness%20fueled%20AI%20lookalikes.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22hchandonnet%40insider.com%20(Henry%20Chandonnet)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Meet%20Andrea%20Ghez%3A%20The%20puzzle-loving%20child%20who%20grew%20up%20to%20discover%20the%20Milky%20Way's%20super