%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1236783605%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Prime%20Video%20is%20doubling%20down%20on%20its%20ambition%20to%20become%20a%20unified%20entertainment%20destination%20across%20Asia-Pacific%2C%20with%20executives%20highlighting%20the%20company%E2%80%99s%20expanding%20ecosystem%20strategy%20during%20the%20APOS%20conference%20session%20%E2%80%9CThe%20APAC%20Playbook%3A%20How%20Prime%20Video%20Is%20Shaping%20Streaming%E2%80%99s%20Future.%E2%80%9D%20Gaurav%20Gandhi%2C%20VP%20of%20APAC%20and%20ANZ%20at%20Prime%20Video%2C%20described%20the%20region%20as%20a%20powerful%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Naman%20Ramachandran%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Morningstar%20thinks%20SpaceX%20stock%20is%20wildly%20overvalued%20%E2%80%94%20but%20says%20there%20are%202%20ways%20the%20company%20can%20change%20its%20mind%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%228192%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22spacex%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a3185bde826bfa433d6e918%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225464%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ESpaceX%20closed%20Tuesday%20at%20about%20%24200%2C%20well%20above%20Morningstar's%20fair%20value%20estimate%20of%20%2463.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EShares%20have%20defied%20doubters%20and%20stayed%20strong%20since%20the%20company's%20historic%20IPO%20last%20week.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EA%20Morningstar%20aerospace%20and%20defense%20analyst%20details%20two%20things%20that%20could%20get%20him%20to%20raise%20his%20estimate.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ELeading%20up%20to%20SpaceX's%20IPO%20last%20Friday%2C%20Morningstar%20analysts%20said%20the%20company's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspacex-ipo-valuation-starlink-grok-elon-musk-ai-morningstar-spcx-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efair%20value%20was%20about%2050%25%20lower%3C%2Fa%3E%20than%20its%20valuation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20its%20first%20three%20trading%20days%2C%20which%20saw%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspacex-spcx-top-investors-first-day-trading-takeaways-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESpaceX%20soar%2049%25%20to%20%24201.68%20a%20share%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20that%20gap%20has%20grown%20to%20nearly%2070%25%2C%20with%20Morningstar%20pegging%20SpaceX's%20fair%20value%20at%20%2463%20a%20share.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20doesn't%20necessarily%20mean%20Morningstar%20is%20calling%20for%20the%20stock%20to%20drop.%20On%20the%20contrary%2C%20Nicolas%20Owens%2C%20its%20aerospace%20and%20defense%20analyst%2C%20thinks%20the%20stock%20could%20continue%20its%20surge%20in%20the%20months%20ahead%20purely%20thanks%20to%20market%20economics%20and%20investor%20sentiment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20investor%20enthusiasm%20could%20last%20indefinitely%2C%20and%20I%20think%20if%20you%20look%20at%20the%20market%20cap%20of%20Tesla%20over%20time%2C%20it%20shows%20that%20there's%20likely%20to%20be%20strong%20demand%20for%20these%20shares%20over%20the%20course%20of%20the%20next%20year%2C%26quot%3B%20Owens%20told%20Business%20Insider%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20at%20these%20prices%2C%20he%20argues%20investors%20are%20pricing%20in%20%26quot%3Bmoonshot%26quot%3B%20scenarios%20for%20the%20company's%20business%20lines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20he%20sees%20SpaceX%20eventually%20gaining%20around%204%25%20of%20the%20total%20data%20center%20compute%20market%20through%20launching%20data%20centers%20into%20space.%20In%20his%20most%20optimistic%20scenario%2C%20which%20investors%20seem%20to%20be%20pricing%20in%20and%20which%20he%20assigns%20only%20a%207%25%20chance%20of%20occurring%2C%20the%20company%20will%20capture%2021%25%20of%20the%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Owens%20remains%20skeptical%20about%20SpaceX's%20valuation%2C%20which%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspacex-stock-market-valuation-surpass-amazon-elon-musk-jeff-bezos-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Enow%20larger%20than%20Amazon's%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20he%20said%20there%20are%20two%20things%20he'll%20be%20watching%20that%20will%20drive%20any%20potential%20upward%20readjustments%20to%20his%20fair%20value%20estimate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226feb786f-8e50-4149-988f-605792bd07e9%5C%22%3ETwo%20ways%20Morningstar%20could%20move%20SpaceX's%20fair%20value%20up%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Cstrong%3Efirst%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20is%20whether%20having%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-ai-data-centers-spacex-will-send-into-space-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edata%20centers%20in%20space%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20if%20it%20proves%20possible%20from%20an%20engineering%20standpoint%20%E2%80%94%20becomes%20more%20cost-effective%20for%20companies%20than%20simply%20having%20their%20data%20centers%20on%20the%20ground.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20touted%20benefits%20of%20putting%20data%20centers%20into%20space%20are%20that%20they%20could%20be%20powered%20by%20solar%20energy%20without%20paying%20for%20cooling.%20That%20would%2C%20in%20theory%2C%20be%20a%20huge%20cost%20relief%20as%20data%20center%20energy%20needs%20are%20enormous.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20economics%20of%20such%20a%20proposition%20have%20yet%20to%20be%20laid%20out%20plainly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20it%20isn't%20financially%20competitive%20with%20the%20terrestrial%20data%20center%2C%20then%20there's%20no%20point%2C%26quot%3B%20Owens%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESecond%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20Owens%20will%20be%20waiting%20to%20see%20if%20SpaceX's%20Starship%20rocket%20becomes%20rapidly%20reusable%2C%20allowing%20it%20to%20carry%20more%20Starlink%20satellites%2C%20and%20potentially%20data%20center%20satellites%2C%20into%20space.%20The%20company%20is%20hoping%20to%20launch%20350%20rockets%20a%20year%2C%20up%20from%20around%20165%20currently.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspacex-starship-open-the-moon-for-business-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EStarship%20rocket%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20has%20undergone%2012%20test%20launches%20so%20far%2C%20is%20bigger%20than%20SpaceX's%20Falcon%20rocket%2C%20which%20will%20give%20the%20company%20the%20capacity%20to%20launch%20more%20satellites%20per%20launch%2C%20effectively%20reducing%20their%20costs.%20So%20far%2C%20the%20rocket's%20boosters%20are%20reusable%2C%20but%20the%20upper%20part%20of%20the%20rocket's%20heat%20shield%20tiles%20are%20not%20yet%20reusable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Starship%20being%20reusable%20is%20really%20important%20because%20they%20can't%20do%20hundreds%20and%20hundreds%20of%20launches%20to%20get%20thousands%20of%20satellites%20up%20in%20space%20without%20a%20reusable%20ship%2C%20and%20it's%20not%20just%20reusable%20at%20all%2C%26quot%3B%20Owens%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20these%20projects%20are%20realized%2C%20or%20simply%20the%20probability%20of%20them%20being%20realized%20rises%2C%20Owens%20said%20SpaceX's%20Morningstar%20fair%20value%20estimate%20could%20rise.%20That%20doesn't%20mean%2C%20however%2C%20that%20SpaceX%20shares%20would%20necessarily%20climb%2C%20as%20these%20upside%20scenarios%20are%20already%20baked%20into%20the%20firm's%20stock%20price.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20market%20seems%20to%20assume%20that%20it's%20already%20a%20done%20deal%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Owen's%20fair%20value%20estimate%20for%20SpaceX%20is%20not%20a%20price%20target%20nor%20a%20call%20on%20where%20its%20share%20price%20will%20go%2C%20he%20has%20written%20in%20recent%20Morningstar%20reports%20that%20he%20expects%20better%20entry%20points%20for%20investors%20going%20forward.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspacex-stock-price-overvalued-ipo-starship-rocket-data-centers-