0luxury.%20They%20are%20as%20necessary%20as%20education.%20Education%20keeps%20a%20child%20in%20school.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F334155%2Fbengaluru-ngo-dream-a-dream-educates-underprivileged-children-life-skills-happiness-curriculum-delhi%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFootball%20keeps%20a%20child%20alive%20with%20hope%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Together%2C%20they%20change%20lives%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAll%20images%20courtesy%3A%20OSCAR%20Foundation.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1757298600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Ffootball-2_11zon-1757076501.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D496964%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ashok%20Rathod%20founded%20the%20OSCAR%20Foundation%20in%20Mumbai%20to%20keep%20children%20away%20from%20addiction%2C%20dropouts%2C%20and%20child%20marriage.%20With%20its%20%E2%80%98No%20School%2C%20No%20Football%E2%80%99%20rule%2C%20the%20foundation%20blends%20education%20and%20sport%2C%20empowering%20thousands%20of%20children%20to%20dream%2C%20learn%2C%20and%20lead.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F496964%2Foscar-foundation-ashok-rathod-football-sports-education-underprivileged-children-mumbai%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%228%20Free%20YouTube%20Channels%20Helping%20Students%20in%20the%20Remotest%20Corners%20of%20India%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFor%20students%20in%20rural%20India%2C%20access%20to%20quality%20education%20often%20comes%20with%20challenges%20%E2%80%94%20limited%20resources%2C%20fewer%20teachers%2C%20and%20the%20absence%20of%20coaching%20centres.%20But%20with%20free%20internet%20and%20smartphones%2C%20YouTube%20has%20turned%20into%20a%20digital%20classroom%20for%20millions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%