kshaw%20or%20a%20state%20transport%20bus%20to%20Karnala%20Bird%20Sanctuary%2C%20located%20about%2013%20km%20from%20Panvel.%20A%20rickshaw%20costs%20around%20Rs%20250%20one%20way%2C%20while%20a%20bus%20or%20shared%20rickshaw%20will%20cost%20under%20Rs%2030%20per%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEntry%20to%20the%20sanctuary%20is%20Rs%2060%20for%20adults%20and%20Rs%2030%20for%20children.%20There%20is%20also%20a%20small%20refundable%20deposit%20for%20plastic%20bottles%2C%20as%20the%20park%20strictly%20enforces%20a%20no-plastic%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpend%20the%20day%20walking%20through%20the%20sanctuary%E2%80%99s%20shaded%20trails.%20Home%20to%20over%20150%20species%20of%20resident%20and%20migratory%20birds%2C%20including%20the%20Malabar%20grey%20hornbill%2C%20golden%20oriole%2C%20and%20paradise%20flycatcher%2C%20it%20is%20a%20place%20for%20nature%20lovers.%20Benches%20are%20placed%20along%20the%20paths%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F413732%2Fkoynanagar-young-guides-are-reviving-tourism-and-creating-jobs-homestays%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eideal%20for%20resting%20and%20birdwatching%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-09-01T214237.289_11zon-1756743171.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Karnala%20Fort%20trail%20begins%20inside%20the%20sanctuary%3B%20Picture%20source%3A%20Mumbai%20Pune%20Adventures%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-09-01T214237.289_11zon-1756743171.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook